over%20crime%20and%20unreliable%20medical%20services.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20follows%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftravel.state.gov%2Fcontent%2Ftravel%2Fen%2Ftraveladvisories%2Ftraveladvisories%2Fthe-bahamas-travel-advisory.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ewarning%20about%20the%20Bahamas%2C%20%3C%2Fa%3Ewhich%20remains%20at%20a%20Level%202%20advisory%2C%20urging%20increased%20caution%20after%20a%20series%20of%20murders.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20embassy%20in%20Jamaica%20warned%20of%20home%20invasions%2C%20armed%20robberies%2C%20sexual%20assaults%2C%20and%20homicides.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESexual%20assaults%20have%20been%20reported%20at%20all-inclusive%20holiday%20resorts%2C%20said%20the%20State%20Department's%20Jamaica%20travel%20advisory.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20also%20noted%3A%20%26quot%3BThe%20homicide%20rate%20reported%20by%20the%20Government%20of%20Jamaica%20has%20for%20several%20years%20been%20among%20the%20highest%20in%20the%20Western%20Hemisphere.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFurthermore%2C%20it%20said%20Jamaican%20police%20often%20do%20not%20respond%20effectively%20to%20serious%20criminal%20incidents%2C%20and%20hospitals%20and%20ambulances%20may%20not%20always%20provide%20reliable%20services%2C%20with%20some%20private%20institutions%20requiring%20upfront%20payments.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20cost%20of%20air%20ambulance%20services%20from%20the%20Caribbean%20to%20the%20US%20can%20range%20from%20%2430%2C000%20to%20%2450%2C000%2C%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20State%20Department's%20warning%20to%20US%20visitors%20is%20important%20because%20tourism%20is%20a%20vital%20economic%20driver%20for%20Jamaica%2C%20the%20largest%20island%20in%20the%20Caribbean.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt%20recorded%204%2C122%2C100%20visitors%20from%20January%20to%20December%202023%20%E2%80%94%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.jaxfaxmagazine.com%2F2023%2F11%2F02%2Fjamaica-expects-record-number-of-visitors-in-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%