2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3Cli%3ECochrin%20said%20TikTok%20users%20help%20each%20other%20find%20affordable%20solutions%20when%20possible.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%3C%2Ful%3E%3Cp%3ELast%20year%2C%20when%20Grace%20Cochrin's%20father%20retired%2C%20she%20lost%20her%20parent-supported%20health%20insurance%20and%20got%20her%20own.%20But%20even%20with%20insurance%2C%20she%20said%20the%20costs%20of%20managing%20her%20type%201%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ediabetes%20are%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAmerican's%20spending%20on%20insulin%20has%20tripled%20in%20the%20past%20decade%2C%20rising%20from%20%248%20billion%20in%202012%20to%20%2422.3%20billion%20in%202022%2C%20according%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiabetes.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fnew-american-diabetes-association-report-finds-annual-costs-diabetes-be%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EAmerican%20Diabetes%20Association%3C%2Fa%3E.%20Factors%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20higher%20costs%20include%20limited%20flexibility%20for%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov%2Fpmc%2Farticles%2FPMC8597930%2F%23%3A~%3Atext%3DStructural%2520factors%2520that%2520contribute%2520to%2Cnegotiations%2520with%2520pharmacy%2520benefit%2520managers.%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efederal%20government%20to%20negotiate%20drug%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20along%20with%20a%20lack%20of%20pricing%20transparency%20in%20talks%20with%20pharmacy%20benefit%20managers%2C%20according%20to%20the%20National%20Institutes%20of%20Health.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Finsulin-lifesaving-prescription-drug-so-expensive-pharma-industry-2019-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20drug%20is%20cheap%20to%20produce%3C%2Fa%3E%20but%20is%20often%20sold%20for%20a%20significant%20profit%20by%20manufacturers.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EPresident%20Joe%20Biden%20tried%20to%20address%20the%20issue%20in%20August%202022%20with%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%2C%20which%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhouse-republicans-voted-biden-build-back-better-prescription-drugs-insulin-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ecapped%20insulin%20costs%20at%20%2435%20a%20month%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20all%20seniors%20on%20Medicare.%20In%20the%20past%20year%2C%20pressure%20from%20the%20White%20House%20and%20the%20public%20pushed%20major%20insulin%20manufacturers%20like%20Eli%20Lilly%20and%20Sanofi%20to%20also%20adopt%20the%20cap%20for%20all%20patients%20with%20private%20insurance%20and%20uninsured%20patients%20who%20enroll%20in%20manufacturer%20assistance%20programs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20others%2C%20like%2025-year-old%20Cochrin%2C%20are%20still%20seeking%20some%20relief%20for%20the%20costs%20of%20insulin%20and%20other%20necessary%20diabetes%20tools%2C%20like%20insulin%20pumps%20and%20continuous%20glucose%20monitors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThat%20insulin%20price%20cap%20was%20huge%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20the%20only%20thing%20for%20so%20many%20diabetics%20that%20is%20expensive%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cochrin%2C%20a%20Charlotte%2C%20North%20Carolina-based%20nurse%20who%20was%20diagnosed%20when%20she%20was%207.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EBeyond%20insulin%2C%20Cochrin%20needs%20to%20afford%20medical%20supplies%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENearly%209%20million%20people%20across%20the%20country%20rely%20on%20insulin%20to%20live%2C%20with%20as%20many%20as%20one%20in%20four%20being%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdiabetic-diabetes-price-of-insulin-buying-groceries-killing-people-pharma-2021-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eunable%20to%20pay%20for%20the%20medicine%20they%20need%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20the%20costs%20of%20insulin%20have%20skyrocketed%2C%20and%20the%20direct%20medical%20costs%20of%20treating%20diabetes%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fdiabetes.org%2Fnewsroom%2Fpress-releases%2Fnew-american-diabetes-association-report-finds-annual-costs-diabetes-be%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ehave%20also%20increased%20by%20about%207%25%3C%2Fa%3E%20since%202017.%20This%20includes%20the%20costs%20of%20prescriptions%2C%20medical%20visits%2C%20and%20medical%20devices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey%20are%20necessary%20for%20quality%20of%20life%20and%20not%20finding%20yourself%20in%20the%20hospital%20every%20few%20weeks%2C%26quot%3B%20Cochrin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20day%2C%20Cochrin%20doses%20insulin%20through%20her%20Omnipod%2C%20a%20small%20insulin%20pump%20attached%20to%20her%20arm%20that%20she%20must%20replace%20every%20three%20days.%20She%20also%20tracks%20blood%20sugar%20changes%20with%20a%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20can%20stay%20alive%20with%20just%20her%20insulin%20%E2%80%94%20which%20costs%20her%20about%20%2425%20a%20month%20%E2%80%94%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ebut%20she%20said%20her%20diabetes%20will%20not%20be%20well%20controlled%20if%20she%20can't%20also%20get%20her%20insulin%20pump%20and%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%20at%20reasonable%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20example%2C%20a%20glucose%20monitor%20might%20wake%20her%20up%20with%20an%20alert%20if%20her%20blood%20sugar%20drops%20to%20a%20dangerous%20level%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%20her%20sleep.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20not%20rationing%20things%20in%20a%20serious%20way%2C%20but%20I%20am%20kind%20of%20being%20more%20mindful%20of%20the%20supplies%20I'm%20using%20and%20trying%20to%20make%20things%20last%20longer%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Cochrin%2C%20who%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.tiktok.com%2F%40grace_oliviat1d%3Flang%3Den%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrequently%20posts%20TikToks%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20her%20experience%20navigating%20the%20healthcare%20system%20as%20a%20diabetic.%20%26quot%3BIt's%20how%20I%20push%20off%20spending%20all%20that%20money%20all%20at%20once.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEarlier%20this%20month%2C%20Cochrin%20posted%20a%20TikTok%20explaining%20that%20a%203-month%20supply%20of%20her%20insulin%20pumps%20would%20cost%20her%20%241%2C800%2C%20even%20after%20insurance.%20Cochrin%20ended%20up%20borrowing%20Omnipods%20from%20another%20TikTok%20user%20and%20plans%20to%20replace%20them%20when%20she%20receives%20her%20next%20prescription.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe%20said%20her%20community%20sometimes%20has%20to%20rely%20on%20each%20other%20to%20fill%20gaps%20in%20supply%20access%2C%20and%20Cochrin%20has%20had%20situations%20where%20she%20temporarily%20switched%20to%20manual%20insulin%20injection%20when%20insulin%20pump%20supplies%20weren't%20available.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECochrin's%20expenses%20can%20be%20unpredictable.%20Her%20continuous%20glucose%20monitor%20doesn't%20cost%20her%20anything%20right%20now%2C%20but%20in%20the%20past%2C%20she%20paid%20%2430%20a%20month%20with%20insurance.%20A%20blood%20sugar%20meter%20is%20also%20around%20%2430%2C%20and%20test%20strips%20are%20almost%20%241%20each.%20If%20Cochrin's%20glucose%20monitor%20isn't%20working%2C%20she%20can%20use%20five%20to%2010%20test%20strips%20per%20day%2C%20and%20she%20estimates%20the%20device%20she%20uses%20to%20prick%20her%20finger%20is%20%2412.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20make%20matters%20worse%2C%20Cochrin's%20doctors%20often%20prescribe%20insulin%20that%20her%20insurance%20doesn't%20cover.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDifferent%20people%20may%20have%20increased%20sensitivity%20to%20different%20types%20and%20brands%20of%20insulin%2C%20Cochrin%20said%2C%20but%20insurance%20companies%20sometimes%20only%20offer%20one%20option%20for%20coverage.%20She%20had%20been%20using%20the%20insulin%20brand%20Novolog%20for%20years%20before%20her%20new%20insurance%20confirmed%20it%20only%20covers%20Humalog.%20If%20she%20wants%20to%20switch%20back%20Novolog%2C%20she%20has%20to%20get%20special%20authorization%20%E2%80%94%20and%20she%20hopes%20the%20price%20won't%20go%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20living%20with%20an%20illness%20for%2018%20years%2C%20they're%20all%20of%20the%20sudden%20going%20to%20tell%20me%20what%20I%20can%20and%20can't%20use%2C%20which%20is%20just%20mind-boggling%20to%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Cochrin%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ECochrin%20said%20she%20often%20feels%20like%20the%20%26quot%3Bmiddleman%26quot%3B%20between%20her%20healthcare%20providers%20and%20her%20insurance%20company.%20She%20makes%20between%2015%20and%2020%20calls%20a%20month%20to%20her%20doctor%2C%20pharmacist%2C%20and%20insurance%20company%20about%20when%20her%20supplies%20will%20be%20available%2C%20where%20she%20can%20pick%20them%20up%2C%20and%20whether%20her%20healthcare%20plan%20will%20cover%20the%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EShe's%20still%20in%20the%20first%20few%20months%20of%20using%20her%20own%20insurance%20plan%20but%20expects%20to%20pay%20up%20to%20%243%2C000%20before%20reaching%20her%20deductible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EInsulin%20cap%20signals%20progress%2C%20but%20diabetics%20still%20need%20cost%20relief%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%2435%20insulin%20cap%20is%20a%20step%20in%20the%20right%20direction%20for%20diabetes%20care%2C%20but%20only%20a%20patchwork%20solution%2C%20said%20Campbell%20Hutton%2C%20the%20vice%20president%20of%20regulatory%20and%20health%20policy%20at%20JDRF%2C%20a%20nonprofit%20research%20and%20advocacy%20organization%20for%20type%201%20diabetes.%20Individuals%20should%20be%20able%20to%20choose%20the%20supplies%20that%20work%20best%20for%20them%20at%20a%20consistently%20affordable%20cost%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20not%20yet%20data%20to%20show%20the%20full%20impact%20of%20the%20insulin%20price%20cap%2C%20but%202023%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hhs.gov%2Fabout%2Fnews%2F2023%2F01%2F24%2Fnew-hhs-report-finds-major-savings-americans-who-use-insulin-thanks-president-bidens-inflation-reduction-act.html%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ereports%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Health%20and%20Human%20Services%3C%2Fa%3E%20suggest%20early%20beneficiaries%20of%20the%20Inflation%20Reduction%20Act%20could%20save%20over%20%24500%20a%20year%20on%20insulin.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMeanwhi