20recent%20years%2C%20the%20widespread%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fonline-sports-betting-legalization-number-of-states-gold-rush-frictionless-2022-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Elegalization%20of%20sports%20betting%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20led%20many%20people%20to%20get%20in%20on%20the%20action.%20Twenty%20percent%20of%20Americans%20wagered%20on%20sports%20over%20the%20prior%2012%20months%2C%20according%20to%20an%20American%20Gaming%20Association%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresources%2Famerican-attitudes-2023%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurvey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%202%2C000%20US%20adults%20conducted%20last%20August.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3ESports%20betting%20is%20now%20legal%20in%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresearch%2Fstate-gaming-map%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E38%3C%2Fa%3E%20states%2C%20up%20from%20only%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.americangaming.org%2Fresources%2Fayearofsportsbetting%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eeight%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202019.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EYoung%20people%2C%20in%20particular%2C%20have%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fhow-sports-betting-fantasy-games-taking-over-college-campuses-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Etaken%20to%20sports%20gambling%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20A%20NCAA%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ncaa.org%2Fnews%2F2023%2F5%2F24%2Fmedia-center-ncaa-releases-sports-wagering-survey-data.aspx%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Esurvey%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20of%20over%203%2C500%20US-based%2018-to-22-year-olds%20conducted%20last%20April%20found%20that%2058%25%20had%20participated%20in%20at%20least%20one%20sports%20betting%20activity.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20many%20individuals%2C%20sports%20betting%20provides%20harmless%20entertainment.%20But%2C%20for%20some%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-addiction-warns-bettors-lose-money-march-madness-2023-3%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egambling%20can%20develop%20into%20an%20addiction%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20can%20result%20in%20the%20loss%20of%20substantial%20sums%20of%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESixteen%20percent%20of%20the%20respondents%20in%20the%20NCAA%20survey%20%E2%80%94%20or%20roughly%20a%20quarter%20of%20those%20who'd%20bet%20on%20sports%20%E2%80%94%20said%20they'd%20engaged%20in%20at%20least%20one%20%26quot%3Brisky%26quot%3B%20gambling%20behavior.%20The%20survey%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fncaaorg.s3.amazonaws.com%2Fresearch%2Fwagering%2FApr2023NCAA_WageringKeyFindings.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edefined%3C%2Fa%3E%20this%20as%20betting%20a%20few%20times%20a%20week%20or%20daily%2C%20betting%20%2450%20or%20more%20on%20the%20typical%20wager%2C%20or%20losing%20over%20%24500%20in%20a%20single%20day.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20shared%20with%20Business%20Insider%20his%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Etop%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eadvice%20for%20new%20sports%20bettors%2C%20including%20what%20traps%20to%20avoid.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E1.%20Don't%20bet%20more%20than%20you're%20willing%20to%20lose%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20said%20establishing%20a%20bankroll%20and%20unit%20size%20are%20important%20steps%20for%20new%20bettors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Flocal%2Flifestyle%2Ffirst-time-gambling-tips%2Fb8274mv%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebankroll%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20is%20how%20much%20money%20someone%20plans%20to%20bet%20over%20a%20specified%20period%2C%20whether%20it%20be%20a%20day%2C%20a%20week%2C%20or%20a%20month.%20The%20unit%20size%20is%20the%20percent%20of%20the%20bankroll%20%E2%80%94%20Jimmy%20said%20ideally%20it's%201%25%20%E2%80%94%20that%20gamblers%20dedicate%20to%20the%20typical%20bet.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20crucial%20to%20make%20sure%20one's%20bankroll%20isn't%20too%20high%2C%20Jimmy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWhatever%20your%20bankroll%20is%2C%20it%20should%20be%20in%20your%20mind%20that%20you%20may%20lose%20it%2C%26quot%3B%20Jimmy%20said.%20%26quot%3BYou%20shouldn't%20bet%20what%20you%20can't%20afford.%20So%20if%20you're%20betting%20with%20your%20house%20or%20your%20car%20payment%20or%20your%20kids'%20college%20fund%2C%20you%20already%20lost.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E2.%20Don't%20just%20bet%20on%20the%20most%20popular%20sports%20and%20games%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20betting%20on%20big%20games%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsports-betting-companies-record-number-betting-on-super-bowl-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3ESuper%20Bowl%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20might%20be%20fun%2C%20Jimmy%20said%20these%20games%20are%20often%20less%20profitable.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%2C%20as%20a%20game%20receives%20more%20wagers%2C%20the%20sportsbooks%20have%20more%20data%20at%20their%20disposal%20to%20make%20the%20odds%20as%20accurate%20as%20possible.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20people%20that%20bet%20in%20a%20sportsbook%2C%20they're%20taking%20that%20information%20and%20turning%20it%20into%20their%20algorithm%20and%20that's%20how%20they%20create%20the%20market%20price%2C%26quot%3B%20Jimmy%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAnd%20given%20high-profile%20games%20tend%20to%20have%20the%20most%20money%20on%20the%20line%20for%20sportsbooks%2C%20Jimmy%20said%20they%20tend%20to%20dedicate%20more%20of%20their%20resources%20to%20getting%20their%20betting%20odds%20right.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20why%20Jimmy%20recommended%20new%20bettors%20focus%20more%20on%20sports%20and%20bets%20that%20receive%20less%20attention.%20Rather%20than%20betting%20on%20the%20NBA%2C%20look%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fafrica.businessinsider.com%2Fsports%2Fwnba-salaries-max-out-nearly-dollar865k-less-than-the-nbas-lowest-contracts-players%2Fb4xcnqf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3EWNBA%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20he%20said.%20And%20rather%20than%20simply%20betting%20on%20who%20will%20win%20a%20game%2C%20he%20said%20it's%20better%20to%20dig%20into%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsuper-bowl-prop-bets-celebrity-picks-first-touchdown-rihanna-song-2023-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eprop%20bets%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20which%20allow%20bettors%20to%20wager%20on%20a%20wide%20range%20of%20outcomes%20%E2%80%94%20like%20whether%20a%20player%20will%20get%20more%20or%20less%20than%2010.5%20rebounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20more%20of%20a%20rare%20market%20that%20you%20go%20in%2C%20the%20more%20potential%20profit%20you%20can%20find%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bbecause%20fewer%20people%20are%20betting%2C%20and%20that's%20where%20these%20sportsbooks%20get%20their%20information%20from.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20said%20strategies%20like%20these%20have%20helped%20him%20and%20his%20cousin%20hit%20roughly%2060%25%20of%20their%20bets%20%E2%80%94%20he%20said%20the%20average%20professional%20bettor%20has%20a%20roughly%2055%25%20win%20percentage.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E3.%20Avoid%20parlays%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20said%20he%20sees%20a%20lot%20of%20new%20gamblers%20wager%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fchristian-mccaffrey-touchdown-wins-bettor-500k-14-leg-parlay-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Eparlays%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20combinations%20of%20individual%20bets%20that%20only%20pay%20out%20if%20each%20individual%20bet%20is%20successful.%20Given%20the%20long%20odds%2C%20these%20bets%20can%20be%20very%20profitable%20when%20they%20hit%2C%20but%20Jimmy%20said%20they%20tend%20to%20be%20a%20bad%20investment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThey're%20trying%20to%20bet%20five%2C%20six%20leg%20parlays%20to%20win%20%2450%2C000%20because%20that's%20what%20you%20see%20on%20TikTok%20and%20Instagram%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%20of%20new%20gamblers.%20%26quot%3BThe%20better%20way%20to%20make%20money%20is%20actually%20the%20opposite%2C%20where%20you%20do%20strictly%20individual%20bets.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E4.%20Don't%20mistake%20early%20success%20for%20expertise%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20bettors%20get%20off%20to%20hot%20starts%20when%20they%20begin%20gambling%2C%20but%20Jimmy%20said%20these%20people%20shouldn't%20get%20too%20confident.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20because%20some%20bettors%20are%20just%20getting%20lucky.%20If%20they%20start%20increasing%20their%20bet%20amounts%20before%20they%20have%20a%20proven%20strategy%2C%20this%20could%20come%20back%20to%20bite%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFor%20somebody%20who%20does%20five%20bets%20a%20day%2C%20it%20may%20take%20them%20a%20month%20to%20really%20have%20enough%20data%20of%20bets%20to%20see%20how%20they%20really%20did%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BDon't%20judge%20something%20based%20on%20one%20day.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EJimmy%20said%20he%20makes%20as%20many%20as%20700%20bets%20a%20week%2C%20which%20provides%20him%20a%20solid%20sample%20size%20by%20the%20end%20of%20the%20month%20%E2%80%94%20but%20he%20doesn't%20recommend%20new%20bettors%20gamble%20this%20frequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E5.%20Don't%20chase%20your%20losses%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20a%20hot%20streak%20turns%20into%20a%20cold%20streak%2C%20Jimmy%20said%20it's%20important%20for%20bettors%20not%20to%20increase%20the%20size%20and%20frequency%20of%20their%20bets%20in%20an%20effort%20to%20make%20up%20for%20the%20money%20they%20lost.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20have%20to%20have%20the%20self-control%20to%20not%20chase%20your%20losses%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BWhen%20you're%20losing%2C%20that's%20the%20time%20you%20should%20actually%20lower%20your%20bankroll.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E6.%20Don't%20value%20winning%20over%20your%20mental%20health%3C%2F