%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbaby-names-most-popular-by-decade-2018-5%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Etoo%20easy%20to%20find%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20like%20Pepsi%20or%20a%20football%20fan%20dressed%20up%20on%20game%20day.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEmma%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Eshimmered%20like%20tasteful%20sequins%20on%20a%20vintage%20dress.%20Emma%20was%20as%20magical%20as%20the%20color%20of%20ice.%20Just%20enough%2C%20but%20not%20too%20much.%20The%20truth%20is%20that%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20be%20myself%20anymore%20because%20I%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Five-helped-thousands-of-people-change-their-habits-heres-what-makes-it-so-difficult-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Edidn't%20like%20myself%20very%20much%3C%2Fa%3E.%20I%20was%2014%20years%20old.%20Does%20anyone%20really%20like%20themselves%20at%20that%20age%3F%20What%20I%20longed%20for%20most%20was%20to%20arrive%20home%20from%20summer%20camp%20as%20someone%20new.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMy%20parents%20made%20me%20file%20the%20paperwork%20myself%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20long%20as%20it's%20not%20permanent%20damage%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20my%20mother%20a%20few%20weeks%20later%20when%20I%20announced%20the%20change%20to%20my%20family.%20My%20father%20nodded%20along.%20I%20had%20already%20yanked%20my%20dusty%20backpack%20off%20the%20camp%20bus%20and%20settled%20into%20my%20familiar%20spot%20at%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fhome%2Fbest-dining-table%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ekitchen%20table%3C%2Fa%3E.%20This%20was%20the%20overall%20life%20policy%20of%20my%20parents%20(except%2C%20somehow%2C%20that%20cobalt%20hair%2C%20which%20they%20were%20strongly%20against).%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you%20want%20to%20have%20it%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fwhat-to-know-before-changing-your-name-legally-2018-8%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elegally%20changed%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you'll%20have%20to%20file%20the%20paperwork%20yourself%20though%2C%26quot%3B%20my%20father%20added%2C%20with%20the%20practicality%20of%20a%20lawyer.%20It%20was%20a%20fair%20response%2C%20although%20I%20did%20not%20appreciate%20it%20at%20the%20time.%20He%20knew%20that%20I%20wouldn't%20want%20to%20deal%20with%20that%20paperwork%2C%20and%20he%20wasn't%20about%20to%20do%20it%20for%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ERegardless%2C%20I%20was%20allowed%20to%20evolve.%20My%20folks%20knew%20I%20would%20become%20so%20many%20versions%20of%20myself%2C%20which%20was%20part%20of%20growing%20up.%20We%20are%20all%20still%20developing%20right%20in%20this%20very%20day%2C%20hour%2C%20and%20minute.%C2%A0Emma%20was%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2F4-syllable-baby-names-2018-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emuch%20less%20common%3C%2Fa%3E%20back%20then%20%E2%80%94%20only%20older%20women%20or%20Europeans%20seemed%20to%20share%20my%20moniker.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EThen%20'Friends'%20made%20the%20name%20Emma%20popular%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ELess%20than%20a%20decade%20later%2C%20in%20season%20eight%2C%20Rachel%20(played%20by%20the%20iconic%20Jennifer%20Aniston)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Ffriends-cast-first-episode-finale-2021-reunion-2023-10%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efrom%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Egave%20her%20and%20Ross's%20baby%20the%20very%20same%20name.%20Soon%2C%20little%20Emma%20babies%2C%20inspired%20by%20the%20hit%20TV%20show%2C%20popped%20up%20like%20buttered%20kernels%20at%20a%20multiplex.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20life%20before%20baby%20Geller-Green%2C%20and%20then%20there%20was%20life%20after.%20What%20I%20am%20trying%20to%20say%20is%20this%3A%20%26quot%3BFriends%26quot%3B%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3Echanged%20my%20life%2C%20but%20not%20in%20the%20way%20that%20you%20might%20think.%20Now%2C%20nearly%20every%20time%20I%20set%20foot%20in%20a%20grocery%20store%2C%20I%20hear%2C%20%26quot%3BEmma%2C%20don't%20touch%20that!%26quot%3B%20or%20%26quot%3BNot%20today%2C%20Emma%26quot%3B%20or%20just%20%26quot%3BEmmah!%26quot%3B%20shouted%20freely.%20A%20sticky-faced%20elementary%20schooler%20runs%20by%2C%20sometimes%20stomping%20on%20my%20foot.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAs%20it%20turned%20out%2C%20the%20name%20Emma%20is%20the%20kind%20of%20Wonder%20bread%20that%20you%20can%20find%20on%20a%20middle%20shelf%20at%20Target%2C%20screamed%20by%20overzealous%20parents%20at%20any%20recreational%20soccer%20game.%20I%20can%20spot%20it%20on%20nearly%20every%20class%20list%20at%20my%20children's%20school%2C%20and%20I%20hear%20it%20echoed%20in%20the%20halls%20of%20the%20shopping%20mall%20near%20my%20house.%20It%20is%20featured%20in%20Hollywood%20and%20also%20at%20the%20train-themed%20playground%20in%20Minnetonka%2C%20Minnesota.%20I%20thought%20I%20was%20launching%20an%20era%20of%20rareness%2C%20and%20I%20was%20wrong.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EI'm%20less%20concerned%20about%20standing%20out%20now%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20are%20276%2C660%20people%20in%20the%20US%20with%20the%20first%20name%20Emma%20right%20now.%20Unsurprisingly%2C%20I%20am%20not%20as%20unique%20as%20I%20once%20wanted%20to%20be.%20I%20changed%2C%20and%20the%20world%20changed%2C%20too.%20Sometimes%2C%20these%20things%20collide%20in%20unexpected%20ways.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAll%20of%20this%20would%20have%20bothered%20me%20when%20I%20was%20coming%20of%20age%2C%20but%20not%20anymore.%20Gratefully%2C%20I%20am%20less%20concerned%20about%20standing%20out%2C%20and%20generally%20less%20compelled%20to%20claim%20my%20identity%20either%20way.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20am%20over%2040%2C%20and%20in%20this%20era%2C%20I%20am%20overly%20satisfied%20by%20a%20good%20night's%20sleep.%20I%20am%20lulled%20by%20the%20way%20the%20sunlight%20pours%20through%20my%20window%20just%20so%20at%202%20p.m.%20I%20have%20meaningful%20work%20as%20a%20psychotherapist%2C%20some%20dear%20friendships%2C%20and%20a%20family%20of%20my%20own%20that%20is%20never%2C%20ever%20boring.%20I%20have%20people%20w