%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03134915%2Fimage-1802.png%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%20India%20reported%20more%20than%2014%20lakh%20new%20cancer%20cases%20and%20over%209%20lakh%20deaths%20due%20to%20the%20disease%20in%202022%2C%20said%20the%20World%20Health%20Organization%20(WHO).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20International%20Agency%20for%20Research%20on%20Cancer%20(IARC)%2C%20WHO%E2%80%99s%20cancer%20arm%2C%20unveiled%20a%20report%20highlighting%20the%20prevalence%20and%20patterns%20of%20cancer%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAmong%20Indian%20women%2C%20breast%20and%20cervix%20cancers%20emerged%20as%20the%20most%20common%2C%20constituting%20nearly%2027%25%20and%2018%25%20of%20new%20cases%2C%20respectively%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.newindianexpress.com%2Fnation%2F2024%2FFeb%2F02%2Fover-14-lakh-new-cancer-cases-nine-lakh-deaths-in-india-in-2022-breast-cancer-most-common-among-women%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20news%20agency%20PTI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20men%2C%20lip%20and%20oral%20cavity%20cancers%20and%20lung%20cancers%20took%20the%20lead%2C%20making%20up%2015.6%25%20and%208.5%25%20of%20new%20cases%2C%20according%20to%20the%20IARC%20report.%20The%20report%20also%20shed%20light%20on%20the%20survival%20rates%2C%20revealing%20that%20nearly%2032.6%20lakh%20people%20in%20India%20were%20alive%20within%20five%20years%20of%20a%20cancer%20diagnosis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWHO%20made%20a%20dire%20prediction%2C%20anticipating%20a%2077%25%20surge%20in%20new%20cancer%20cases%20to%20over%2035%20million%20by%202050%2C%20with%20deaths%20nearly%20doubling%20from%202012%20to%20exceed%2018%20million.%20Key%20factors%20contributing%20to%20this%20alarming%20trend%20included%20tobacco%20use%2C%20alcohol%20consumption%2C%20obesity%2C%20population%20aging%2C%20and%20growth.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20India%2C%20the%20risk%20of%20developing%20cancer%20before%20the%20age%20of%2075%20was%20calc