0a%20a%20rule%20of%E2%80%A6%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F4zq4rk0mxi%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F4zq4rk0mxi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Pritesh%20Shah%20(%40priteshshah_)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fpriteshshah_%2Fstatus%2F1753661646021812517%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%203%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CYes%2C%20I%20shot%20(him)%20myself.%20I%20have%20no%20regrets.%20If%20my%20son%20is%20being%20beaten%20in%20front%20of%20the%20police%20inside%20the%20police%20station%2C%20what%20will%20I%20do%2C%E2%80%9D%20asked%20Ganpat%20Gaikwad%20while%20talking%20to%20a%20news%20channel.%20He%20claimed%20that%20he%20fired%20five%20rounds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20Eknath%20Shinde%20is%20attempting%20to%20%E2%80%9Ccreate%20a%20kingdom%20of%20criminals%E2%80%9D%20in%20Maharashtra.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20Datta%20Shinde%2C%20Thane%20Additional%20CP%2C%20said%20that%20the%20incident%20took%20place%20last%20night%20when%20they%20had%20come%20to%20the%20police%20station%20in%20connection%20with%20a%20property%20dispute%20and%20there%20was%20no%20question%20of%20self-defence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThose%20who%20had%20come%20to%20the%20police%20station%20included%20Vaibhav%20Gaikwad%2C%20his%20father%20and%20MLA%20Ganpat%20Gaikwad%20and%20Mahesh%20Gaikwad.%20There%20was%20a%20loud%20conversation%20happening%20outside%20so%20the%20PI%20came%20outside%20to%20try%20and%20make%20people%20understand.%20During%20that%20time%20the%20firing%20took%20place%20inside%20the%20station.%20MLA%20Gaikwad%20shot%20Mahesh%20Gaikwad%20and%20Rahul%20Patil%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20told%20ANI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-width%3D%5C%22550%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%20data-dnt%3D%5C%22true%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FWATCH%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtw