tions%20where%20audiences%20are%20deliberately%20misled%20and%20%E2%80%98misinformation%E2%80%99%20as%20cases%20where%20information%20is%20spread%20out%20of%20genuine%20belief%20but%20which%20can%20have%20harmful%20consequences.%20We%20can%20also%20add%20to%20such%20risks%20the%20deliberate%20erasure%20of%20crucial%20information.%20The%20question%20that%20the%20media%20of%20a%20country%2C%20which%20promotes%20itself%20as%20%E2%80%9CVishwaguru%E2%80%9D%20(teacher%20of%20the%20world)%2C%20should%20ask%20themselves%20is%20this%3A%20What%20happens%20when%20crucially%20important%20stories%20like%20the%20oceanic%20human%20suffering%20in%20Gaza%20or%20the%20ICJ%20ruling%20are%20blanked%20out%20of%20the%20news%20space%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fworld%2Fwhat-explains-the-desensitisation-of-the-western-leadership-towards-horrors-in-gaza%5C%22%3Earticle%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20posed%20a%20parallel%20question%3A%20%E2%80%98What%20Explains%20the%20Desensitisation%20of%20the%20Western%20Leadership%20Towards%20Horrors%20in%20Gaza%3F%E2%80%99%20(January%2027)%20and%20went%20on%20to%20observe%20that%20%E2%80%9CUnlike%20with%20earlier%20conflicts%2C%20this%20time%20we%20are%20able%20to%20see%20footage%20not%20only%20of%20the%20people%20on%20the%20ground%20as%20they%20are%20being%20bombed%20and%20seeing%20their%20lives%20completely%20disrupted%20but%20of%20the%20ones%20at%20the%20top%20doggedly%20supporting%20the%20carnage%20as%20something%20necessary.%E2%80%9D%20The%20western%20media%E2%80%99s%20reporting%20on%20Gaza%20has%20met%20with%20widespread%20criticism.%20Journalist%20Vidya%20Krishnan%20recently%20termed%20it%20%E2%80%9Ca%20textbook%20case%20of%20coloniser%E2%80%99s%20journalism%E2%80%9D%2C%20a%20%E2%80%9Cjournalism%20done%20by%20practitioners%20from%20colonising%20countries%20who%20take%20pride%20in%20their%20imperial%20conquests%20and%20have%20an%20elevated%20sense%20of%20self%2C%20every%20fibre%20nurtured%20by%20centuries%20of%20predatory%20accumulation%20of%20wealth%2C%20knowledge%20and%20privilege%E2%80%9D%20(%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.aljazeera.com%2Fopinions%2F2024%2F2%2F2%2Fwestern-coverage-of-gaza-a-textbook-case-of-colonisers-journalism%23%3A~%3Atext%3DIn%2520their%2520coverage%2520of%2520the%2Cis%2520inflicted%2520by%2520their%2520allies.%5C%22%3E%E2%80%98Western%20coverage%20of%20Gaza%3A%20A%20textbook%20case%20of%20coloniser%E2%80%99s%20journalism%E2%80%99%2C%20%3Cem%3EAl%20Jazeera%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20February%202%3C%2Fa%3E).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIf%20this%20is%20the%20case%20with%20reportage%20from%20London%20and%20New%20York%2C%20how%20should%20we%20define%20coverage%20from%20India%20which%20makes%20its%20statement%20on%20Gaza%20through%20its%20non-reportage%20of%20Gaza%3F%20A%20textbook%20case%20of%20colonised%20journalism%3F%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20grasp%20the%20real-life%20consequences%20of%20such%20media%20silence%2C%20one%20just%20has%20to%20listen%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fisraeli-recruiters-keep-mum-on-job-conditions-as-indian-workers-rush-to-apply%5C%22%3Eworkers%20queuing%20up%20at%20various%20centres%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20facilitated%20by%20India%E2%80%99s%20National%20Skills%20Development%20Corporation%2C%20to%20work%20in%20Israel.%20A%20report%20in%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%20report%20indicates%20the%20blanket%20of%20opacity%20that%20marks%20the%20process.%20Nobody%20has%20any%20idea%20of%20the%20terms%20and%20conditions%20of%20the%20jobs%20that%20await%20them%20in%20Israel%2C%20nor%20do%20they%20have%20an%20inkling%20of%20their%20working%20conditions%20there.%20%3Cem%3EThe%20Guardian%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Fglobal-development%2F2023%2Fdec%2F03%2Falmost-400000-palestinians-have-lost-jobs-due-to-war-report-says%5C%22%3Ehas%20estimated%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20400%2C000%C2%A0Palestinians%20have%20lost%20their%20jobs%20in%20Israel%20post%20October%207%2C%202023%2C%20and%20chances%20are%20that%20these%20Indian%20workers%20probably%20do%20not%20even%20know%20that%20they%20are%20being%20shipped%20in%20to%20replace%20Palestinian%20labour.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDriven%20out%20by%20poverty%20and%20hardships%20at%20home%2C%20an%20extremely%20fraught%20scenario%20awaits%20these%20Indians%2C%20eventually%20estimated%20to%20number%2040%2C000%2C%20with%20their%20own%20government%20not%20bothering%20to%20stand%20guarantor%20for%20their%20safety.%20The%20fog%20created%20by%20misinformation%2C%20disinformation%20and%20obliteration%20of%20information%20have%20contributed%20to%20making%20this%20passage%20rife%20with%20danger.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2B%2B%2B%C2%A0%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EImportance%20of%20calling%20out%20viral%20fictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMore%20dangerous%20than%20the%20toxic%20disinformation%20deliberately%20created%20and%20made%20viral%2C%20is%20the%20public%20silence%20that%20accompanies%20it.%20Three%20well-known%20journalists%20%E2%80%93%20Sreenivasan%20Jain%2C%20Mariyam%20Alavi%20and%20Supriya%20Sharma%20%E2%80%93%20by%20bringing%20out%20a%20book%20on%20the%20phenomenon%20have%20made%20a%20courageous%20effort%20to%20break%20the%20pattern%20of%20public%20apathy%20towards%20fake%20news%20in%20the%20country.%20The%20work%20they%20have%20jointly%20authored%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fbooks%2Fnew-book-debunks-myths-about-love-jihad-muslim-appeasement-and-other-falsehoods-about-minorities%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3ELove%20Jihad%20and%20Other%20Fictions%3C%2Fem%3E%20(Aleph%2C%202024)%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20is%20particularly%20well%20timed%2C%20given%20that%20with%20another%20General%20Election%20on%20the%20horizon%2C%20the%20country%20is%20set%20to%20face%20a%20tsunami%20of%20fake%20information%20promoted%20by%20the%20cash-soaked%20ruling%20party.%20Advances%20in%20information%20technology%2C%20notably%20the%20rise%20of%20Artificial%20Intelligence%2C%20have%20only%20added%20to%20this%20threat.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20dangers%20of%20fake%20news%20are%20obvious.%20By%20becoming%20the%20stuff%20of%20everyday%20conversations%2C%20they%20have%20over%20the%20years%20deepened%20social%20fissures%20and%20spread%20communal%20hatred%20within%20the%20country.%20But%20the%20authors%20also%20point%20to%20impacts%20that%20are%20not%20so%20obvious%2C%20as%20for%20instance%20how%20fake%20content%20created%20and%20spread%20on%20social%20media%20becomes%20the%20foundation%20on%20which%20laws%20are%20made.%20As%20they%20put%20it%3A%20%E2%80%9CToday%E2%80%99s%20WhatsApp%20Forward%2C%20Tomorrow%E2%80%99s%20Law%E2%80%99.%20Himachal%20Pradesh%2C%20then%20under%20BJP%20rule%2C%20was%20the%20first%20Indian%20state%20to%20enact%20a%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20law%20%E2%80%93%20the%20Himachal%20Pradesh%20Freedom%20Of%20Religion%20Act%2C%202019%20(Act%20No.%2013%20of%202019).%20Over%20the%20next%20five%20years%2C%20most%20states%20with%20BJP%20governments%20went%20on%20to%20enact%20such%20laws%20that%20intertwine%20marriage%20with%20religious%20conversion.%20This%20flurry%20of%20law-making%20would%20seem%20to%20indicate%20that%20there%20is%20an%20exponential%20growth%20in%20interfaith%20marriages.%20In%20actual%20fact%2C%20as%20the%20authors%20point%20out%20in%20this%20book%2C%20only%202.5%25%20of%20marriages%20in%20the%20country%20were%20interreligious%2C%20according%20to%202015-2016%20National%20Family%20Health%20Survey%20data.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20book%20maps%20out%20how%20the%20idea%20of%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20gained%20such%20wide%20acceptability.%20One%20of%20the%20sources%20often%20cited%20for%20the%20supposed%20proliferation%20of%20interfaith%20marriages%20was%20a%20special%20edition%20of%20VHP%E2%80%99s%20in-house%20magazine%20which%20%E2%80%9Cdescribed%20this%20strategy%20as%20%E2%80%98demographic%20invasion%E2%80%99%20by%20Muslims%20to%20reduce%20Hindus%20to%20a%20minority%E2%80%9D.%20Deeper%20scrutiny%20into%20the%20magazine%20revealed%20that%20of%20the%20list%20of%20supposedly%20147%20cases%20unearthed%20through%20investigation%20conducted%20by%20the%20VHP%20turned%20out%20to%20be%20a%20compilation%20of%20instances%20drawn%20possibly%20after%20a%20Google%20search.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIncidentally%2C%20%3Cem%3EOpIndia%3C%2Fem%3E%20was%20the%20single%20largest%20contributor%20to%20this%20list!%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAlmost%20half%20the%20cases%20were%20found%20to%20be%20invalid.%C2%A0%20The%20conclusion%20was%20inescapable%3A%20%E2%80%9CThe%20VHP%20list%20(perhaps%20the%20most%20widely%20cited%20source%20to%20buttress%20the%20claim%20that%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20exists)%2C%20offers%20no%20evidence%20of%20a%20Muslim%20conspiracy.%E2%80%9D%20What%20was%20clear%20was%20that%20from%20a%20wide%20catchment%20of%20gender-related%20crimes%20in%20India%2C%20instances%20were%20selected%20which%20involved%20alleged%20crimes%20and%20cases%20of%20misogynistic%20behaviour%20by%20Muslim%20men%20toward%20Hindu%20women%2C%20to%20establish%20the%20%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20thesis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%98Love%20Jihad%E2%80%99%20in%20one%20of%20four%20fictions%20the%20book%20sets%20out%20to%20dismantle.%20Others%20include%20claims%20that%20the%20population%20of%20Muslims%20will%20overtake%20that%20of%20Hindus%20because%20as%20a%20VHP%3Cem%3E%20apparatchik%3C%2Fem%3E%20told%20the%20authors%2C%20Muslims%20%E2%80%9Cbelieve%20in%20procreating%20more%20children%20as%20a%20religious%20duty%E2%80%A6in%20their%20rejection%20of%20population%20control%20methods.%E2%80%9D%20The%20book%20takes%20this%20apart%20by%20citing%20credible%20data.%20The%20same%20scrupulous%20approach%20is%20extended%20to%20exposing%20other%20frequently%20cited%20claims%2C%20including%20those%20of%20forced%20conversions%20and%20Muslim%20appeasement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20outstanding%20graphic%20in%20the%20book%20exposes%20how%20the%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20in%20its%20answers%20to%20parliamentarians%20asking%20for%20data%20of%20illegal%20immigrants%20in%20India%20admitted%20at%20least%2010%20times%20over%20the%20years%20of%20Modi%20rule%20that%20it%20has%20no%20confirmed%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Flegal.economictimes.indiatimes.com%2Fnews%2Flitigation%2Fno-accurate-data-on-all-illegal-immigrants-centre-to-sc%2F105942937%5C%22%3Edata%3C%2Fa%3E%20about%20illegal%20immigrants%20residing%20in%20the%20country.%20However%2C%20this%20has%20never%20stopped%20BJP%20leaders%20from%20making%20wild%20claims%20of%20crores%20of%20%E2%80%9Cinfiltrators%E2%80%9D%20living%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFor%20journalists%20in%20particular%2C%20%3Cem%3ELove%20Jihad%20And%20Other%20Fictions%3C%2Fem%3E%20is%20a%20useful%20work%20to%20access.%20Apart%20from%20being%20a%20rich%20compendium%20of%20slanted%20stories%2C%20cynically%20distorted%20social%20media%20posts%20and%20carefully%20culled%20data%2C%20it%20counters%20the%20falsehoods%20in%20a%20straightforward%20and%20credible%20manner.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHas%20France%20let%20down%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrench%20president%2C%20Emmanuel%20Macron%2C%20went%20back%20to%20France%20with%20one%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fpm-modi-gifts-replica-of-ram-mandir-to-frances-emmanuel-macron-in-jaipur-watch-101706198325756.html%5C%22%3Ereplica%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir%3C%2Fa%3E%3B%20one%20Indo-French%20joint%20venture%20between%20Airbus%20and%20Tata%20for%20the%20manufacture%20of%20civilian%20helicopters%3B%20and%20the%20possibility%20of%20keeping%20alive%20two%20large%20defence%20deals%20running%20into%20several%20billions%20of%20dollars%20to%20manufacture%20Rafale-M%20jets%20for%20the%20Indian%20Navy%20as%20well%20as%20three%20Scorpene-class%20submarines%2C%20both%20of%20which%20had%20been%20in%20the%20pipeline.%20All%20in%20all%2C%20Macron%20had%20every%20reason%20to%20be%20satisfied%20with%20the%20outcome%20of%20his%20latest%20visit%20to%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20was%20just%20a%20small%20fly%20in%20the%20ointment%3A%20India%E2%80%99s%20Union%20Ministry%20of%20Home%20Affairs%20had%20filed%20a%20showcause%20notice%20on%20January%2018%2C%20about%20a%20week%20before%20Macron%20was%20arrive%2C%20against%20French%20journalist%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmha-issues-notice-for-cancelling-french-journalist-oci-card%5C%22%3EVanessa%20Dougnac%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%93%20who%20has%20been%20living%20and%20working%20in%20India%20for%20over%20two%20decades%20and%20is%20married%20to%20an%20Indian%20citizen%20%E2%80%93%20threatening%20to%20revoke%20her%20Overseas%20Citizen%20of%20India%20(OCI)%20card.%C2%A0%20If%20she%20does%20not%20respond%20to%20the%20MHA%20notice%20with%20an%20adequate%20explanation%20by%20February%202%2C%20she%20may%20face%20deportation.%20The%20reason%20for%20the%20action%2C%20according%20to%20%3Cem%3EOpIndia%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20a%20mouthpiece%20of%20the%20current%20political%20dispensation%2C%20was%20because%20of%20her%20%E2%80%9Cmalicious%E2%80%9D%20work%20which%20has%20created%20a%20%E2%80%9Cbiased%20negative%20perception%E2%80%9D%20of%20India%20and%20over%20alleged%20violation%20of%20visa%20rules.%20Besides%20this%2C%20the%20accusation%20was%20made%20about%20her%20work%2C%20that%20it%20provoked%20%E2%80%9Cdisorder%20and%20disturbed%20the%20peace%20in%20certain%20sections%20of%20the%20society.%E2%80%9D%20Vanessa%20Dougnac%2C%20on%20her%20part%2C%20has%20so%20far%20steadfastly%20denied%20all%20the%20charges%20made%20against%20her.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20showcause%20notice%20led%20to%20deep%20consternation%20among%20journalists%20in%20the%20country%2C%20especially%20foreign%20correspondents%2C%2030%20of%20whom%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fstaging.thewire.in%2Fmedia%2Fmacrons-visit-france-raises-expulsion-threat-to-french-journalist-foreign-correspondents-in-india%5C%22%3Ewrote%3C%2Fa%3E%20an%20open%20letter%20of%20protest%20on%20the%20issue.%20In%20the%20letter%2C%20they%20also%20made%20it%20a%20point%20to%20request%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20Indian%20authorities%20to%20facilitate%20the%20vital%20work%20of%20a%20free%20press%20in%20line%20with%20India%E2%80%99s%20democratic%20traditions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFrom%20all%20evidence%2C%20the%20French%20authorities%20did%20raise%20the%20issue%20with%20their%20Indian%20counterparts%2C%20but%20so%20far%2C%20India%20has%20desisted%20from%20rolling%20back%20the%20order.%20Interestingly%2C%20in%20its%20latest%20statement%20on%20the%20issue%2C%20the%20Indian%20spokesperson%20denied%20that%20it%20was%20provoked%20by%20Dougnac%E2%80%99s%20journalism%20and%20this%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20complying%20with%20the%20rules.%20Could%20this%20be%20read%20as%20the%20Indian%20government%20taking%20a%20step%20back%3F%20We%20will%20have%20to%20see%20how%20it%20plays%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EReaders%20write%20in%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESatyameva%20Jayate!%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3EDr%20Naveen%20Kumar%20Vanam%20from%20Hyderabad%20wrote%20in%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CSince%202019%20I%20have%20been%20associated%20with%20the%20RSS%2C%20but%20now%C2%A0I%20am%20away%C2%A0from%20it%20for%20a%20few%20months%C2%A0because%20they%20are%20not%20following%20actual%20Hindutva%20and%20the%20teachings%20of%20the%20%3Cem%3EBhagavad%20Gita%3C%2Fem%3E.%20Governments%20are%20veering%20more%20towards%20religion%20than%20the%20development%20of%20the%20country%2C%20ignoring%20equality%20and%20democracy%20in%20the%20process.%20I%20am%20really%20frustrated%20by%20the%20way%20they%20perceive%20people%20of%20other%20religions%2C%20giving%20more%20weightage%20to%20creed%20and%20creating%20conditions%20for%20future%20religious%20conflicts%20in%20India.%20Many%20of%20these%20issues%20have%20international%20dimensions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20joined%20the%20RSS%20only%20for%20India%E2%80%99s%20growth%2C%20not%20for%20its%20Hindutva%20ideology.%20The%20present%20leader%20is%20not%20ruling%2C%20he%20is%20dictating.%20Controversial%20bills%20are%20being%20brought%20in%2C%20the%20Election%20Commission%20has%20been%20suborned%2C%20people%20should%20realise%20that%20actual%20spirituality%20is%20missing%20from%20the%20actions%20of%20the%20government.%20If%20we%20do%20not%20speak%20out%20today%2C%20it%20is%20likely%20that%20the%20very%20name%20of%20India%20will%20be%20changed%20to%20incorporate%20his%20own%20name.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20personally%20feel%20that%20there%E2%80%99s%20no%20religion%20in%20the%20world%20greater%20than%20humanity.%20May%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETruth%20win!%20Satyameva%20Jayate!%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EReligion%20is%20the%20national%20ideology%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EPradip%20Biswas%20had%20this%20comment%20to%20share%20with%20The%20Wire%E2%80%99s%20readers%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%C2%A0%20%E2%80%9CAfter%20January%2022%2C%20and%20the%20consecration%20of%20the%20Ram%20Temple%2C%20there%20can%20be%20no%20doubt%20that%20religion%20leads%20the%20nation%20now%E2%80%A6%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E1.)%20Jayaram%20has%20this%20to%20say%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%E2%80%9CNot%20one%20Muslim%20among%20the%20Union%20Council%20of%20Ministers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENot%20one%20Muslim%20among%20the%20ruling%20party%20MPs.%20Muslims%20make%20up%2014%20per%20cent%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20population.%20Might%20be%20worth%20bearing%20this%20in%20mind%20in%20the%20context%20of%20the%20January%2022%20circus%20in%20Ayodhya%2FFaizabad.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%2B%2B%2B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWithdraw%20OSB%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cstrong%3EDr.%20Roshmi%20Goswami%2C%20c%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cem%3Eo-chairperson%2C%20and%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Cstrong%3E%3Cem%3EDr.%20P.%20Saravanamuttu%2C%20Bureau%20Member%2C%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3Cem%3ESouth%20Asians%20for%20Human%20Rights%20(SAHR)%2C%20a%20regional%20network%20of%20human%20rights%20defenders%2C%20wrote%20in%20on%20the%20%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsouthasianrights.us11.list-manage.com%2Ftrack%2Fclick%3Fu%3Dcd97a10470ba96056271cd23f%26id%3D6557b0941d%26e%3Dde9a03d0d9%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EOnline%20Safety%20Bill%20(OSB)%2C%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%C2%A0by%20the%20Parliament%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20on%20January%2024%3A%20%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%9CNumerous%20parties%20within%20Sri%20Lanka%20and%20at%20international%20and%20regional%20level%20have%20demanded%20the%20withdrawal%20of%20the%20OSB%2C%20emphasising%20that%20it%20would%20severely%20suppress%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20dissent%E2%80%A6After%20the%20OSB%20was%20tabled%20in%20Parliament%2C%2051%20petitions%20were%20filed%20in%20the%20Supreme%20Court%20challenging%20its%20constitutionality%E2%80%A6%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAcross%20South%20Asia%2C%20there%20are%20legislations%20such%20as%20the%20Digital%20Security%20Act%20of%202018%20and%20the%20Information%20and%20Communications%20Technology%20Act%20(Amended%20in%202009%20and%202013)%20in%20Bangladesh%20as%20well%20as%20colonial%20era%20laws%20such%20as%20Section%20124%20A%20(Sedition)%20of%20Indian%20Penal%20Code%20and%20Pakistan%20Penal%20Code%20and%20the%20Official%20Secrets%20Act%20of%201923%20of%20Pakistan%20and%20Bangladesh%20which%20have%20been%20used%20and%20proven%20to%20effectively%20stifle%20freedom%20of%20expression%20and%20suppress%20dissent.%20SAHR%20is%20concerned%20that%20the%20OSB%20too%20will%20be%20used%20in%20such%20a%20manner%20to%20suppress%20freedom%20of%20expression%20in%20Sri%20Lanka.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CTherefore%2C%20SAHR%20strongly%20calls%20upon%20the%20Government%20of%20Sri%20Lanka%20to%C2%A0repeal%C2%A0the%20OSB%20and%20adhere%20to%20its%20obligations%20as%20a%20state%20party%20to%20the%20International%20Covenant%20of%20Civil%20and%20Political%20Rights%20