0values%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20statement%20read.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20FIR%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%20alleged%20that%20the%20CES%20transferred%20more%20than%20Rs%2032%20lakh%20other%20than%20salaries%20or%20remuneration%20from%20its%20Foreign%20Contribution%20(Regulation)%20Act%20(FCRA)%20account%20to%20other%20accounts%20in%202020%20and%202021%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20Act%2C%C2%A0%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftheprint.in%2Findia%2Fdiverted-rs-43-lakh-for-non-admin-purposes-violated-fcra-rules-cbi-fir-against-harsh-mander%2F1951801%2F%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E%20reported%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEnquiry%20has%20also%20revealed%20that%20%5Bthe%5D%20Centre%20for%20Equity%20Studies%20had%20diverted%20an%20amount%20of%20Rs%2010%2F-%20Lakh%20(approx.)%20from%20its%20FCRA%20account%20through%20the%20firm(s)%20in%20violation%20of%20the%20provisions%20of%20FCRA%2C%202010%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20FIR%20also%20said%20according%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThePrint%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBut%20the%20signatories%20of%20solidarity%20statement%20claimed%20the%20CBI%E2%80%99s%20FIR%20indicated%20Mander%20was%20being%20charged%20%E2%80%9Cwithout%20any%20material%20basis%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20is%20clear%20from%20the%20FIR%20No.%20RC2202024%20E0002%2FEO%20II%2FN.D.%20under%20sections%2035%20r%2Fw%207%2C8%2C12(4)%20(a)%20(vi)%20and%20section%2039%20of%20FCRA%20Act%202010%20invoked%20by%20the%20CBI%2C%20that%20the%20charges%20being%20brought%20under%20Mr%20Mander%20are%20entirely%20fabricated%20and%20without%20any%20material%20basis%2C%E2%80%9D%20they%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20stand%20in%20solidarity%20with%20Dr.%20Mander%2C%20in%20his%20determined%20resolve%20to%20preserve%20the%20principles%20and%20values%20of%20constitutional%20India%2C%E2%80%9D%20their%20letter%20concluded.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMander%20responded%20to%20Fridays%E2%80%99%20raids%20by%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CMy%20life%20and%20my%20work%20are%20my%20only%20response.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20June%202023%2C%20the%20Union%20home%20ministry%20invoked%20Section%203%20of%20the%20FCRA%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Frights%2Ffcra-harsh-mander-think-tank-ces-suspended-columnist%5C%22%3Esuspend%20the%20CES%E2%80%99s%20FCRA%20license%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20section%20bars%20any%20%E2%80%9Ccorrespondent%2C%20columnist%2C%20cartoonist%2C%20editor%2C%20owner%2C%20printer%20or%20publisher%20of%20a%20registered%20newspaper%E2%80%9D%20from%20accepting%20any%20foreign%20contributions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMander%2C%20a%20former%20IAS%20officer%2C%20has%20been%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20the%20campaign%20against%20communal%20disharmony%20in%20India%20and%20has%20been%20severely%20critical%20of%20the%20Modi%20government%20over%20the%20last%20ten%20years%20for%20allegedly%20fuelling%20majoritarian%20politics%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20statement%20of%20solidarity%20is%20reproduced%20in%20full%20below.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%C2%A7%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPress%20statement%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3E2nd%20February%2C%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EOver%20250%20citizens%20condemn%20the%20harassment%20by%20Indian%20State%20agencies%20of%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20Director%20Centre%20for%20Equity%20studies%2C%20New%20Delhi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDemand%20closure%20of%20the%20FIR%20filed%20by%20the%20CBI%20and%20all%20other%20investigations%20underway%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20the%20undersigned%20unequivocally%20condemn%20the%20continued%20victimisation%20and%20intimidation%20of%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Mander.%20We%20are%20deeply%20disturbed%20by%20the%20raid%20on%20the%20morning%20of%202nd%20February%2C%202024%20at%20the%20residence%20of%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Mander%20and%20ongoing%20raid%20on%20the%20Centre%20for%20Equity%20Studies%2C%20the%20organisation%20founded%20by%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Mander.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHarsh%20Mander%20is%20a%20widely%20respected%20and%20internationally%20acclaimed%20human%20rights%20activist%20who%20has%20taken%20up%20issues%20of%20those%20most%20oppressed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EToday%E2%80%99s%20raid%20is%20a%20part%20of%20the%20long%20chain%20of%20harassment%20of%20Dr.%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20his%20colleagues%2C%20his%20family%20and%20former%20and%20present%20board%20members%20of%20the%20Centre%20for%20Equity%20Studies.%20It%20is%20important%20to%20know%20that%20since%202020%20multiple%20investigating%20agencies%20of%20the%20Government%20including%20National%20Commission%20for%20the%20Protection%20of%20Child%20Rights%20(NCPCR)%2C%20Delhi%20Police%E2%80%99s%20Economic%20offences%20wing%2C%20Income%20Tax%20(IT)%20authorities%2C%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20(ED)%20and%20now%20the%20Central%20Bureau%20of%20Investigations%20(CBI)%20have%20been%20carrying%20out%20what%20can%20only%20be%20described%20as%20a%20vindictive%20witch%20hunt.%20In%20not%20a%20single%20case%20has%20a%20chargesheet%20been%20presented%20in%20a%20court%20of%20law.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20egregious%20attacks%20on%20Harsh%20Mander%20and%20the%20CES%20are%20an%20attack%20on%20all%20of%20civil%20society%20in%20India%20and%20all%20those%20who%20work%20to%20promote%20constitutional%20values.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20is%20clear%20from%20the%20FIR%20No.%20RC2202024%20E0002%2FEO%20II%2FN.D.%20under%20sections%2035%20r%2Fw%207%2C8%2C12(4)%20(a)%20(vi)%20and%20section%2039%20of%20FCRA%20Act%202010%20invoked%20by%20the%20CBI%2C%20that%20the%20charges%20being%20brought%20under%20Mr%20Mander%20are%20entirely%20fabricated%20and%20without%20any%20material%20basis.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20demand%20the%20closure%20of%20all%20investigations%20including%20the%20CBI%20FIR%20against%20Harsh%20Mander%2C%20his%20colleagues%20and%20the%20CES.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESpeaking%20on%20the%20raids%2C%20Dr.%20Mander%20said%20that%20he%20was%20further%20strengthened%20in%20his%20resolve%20and%20a