p%3EFinance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%E2%80%99s%20shortest%20budget%20speech%20(56%20minutes)%20was%20largely%20about%20reiterating%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20It%20is%20another%20matter%20that%20many%20of%20the%20key%20achievements%20cited%20did%20not%20have%20the%20backing%20of%20data%20or%20facts.%20But%20facts%20have%20never%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20penchant%20for%20weaving%20self-congratulatory%20narratives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20most%20astounding%20claim%20the%20finance%20minister%20made%20was%20that%20average%20real%20incomes%20have%20gone%20up%20by%2050%25%20during%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20tenure.%20This%20flies%20in%20the%20face%20of%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20own%20data%20sets%20formally%20released%20some%20time%20ago%20stating%20that%20regular%20average%20monthly%20wages%20in%20India%20have%20stagnated%20at%20around%20Rs%2020%2C000%20for%20five%20years.%20It%20was%20Rs%2019%2C450%20in%202017-18%20and%20Rs%2020%2C039%20in%202022-23%2C%20as%20per%20the%20recently%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Flabour%2Fvideo-santosh-mehrotra-unemployment-unpaid-worker%5C%22%3Ereleased%3C%2Fa%3E%20Periodic%20Labour%20Force%20Survey%20(PLFS).%20Real%20wages%20have%20actually%20declined%20by%20over%2025%25%20in%20five%20years.%20Given%20this%20data%20released%20by%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20it%20is%20astonishing%20that%20the%20finance%20minister%20should%20make%20a%20claim%20of%2050%25%20growth%20in%20real%20incomes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20near%20consensus%20among%20economists%2C%20including%20among%20those%20well%20disposed%20towards%20the%20Modi%20regime%2C%20that%20real%20rural%20wages%20have%20stagnated%20for%20years.%20This%20income%20stagnation%20has%20reflected%20in%20the%20stagnation%20in%20private%20consumption%20over%20the%20past%20several%20years.%20Private%20consumption%2C%20the%20main%20driver%20of%20GDP%20growth%20in%20India%2C%20has%20grown%20at%20about%203%25%20on%20average%20annually%20in%20the%20past%20five%20years.%20This%20data%2C%20too%2C%20is%20corroborated%20by%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Statistics%20and%20Programme%20Implementation.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20broadly%2C%20there%20is%20evidence%20of%20stagnation%20in%20income%20and%20consumption.%20There%20is%20also%20consensus%20within%20the%20industry%20that%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.nytimes.com%2F2024%2F01%2F02%2Fbusiness%2Findia-economy-foreign-direct-investment.html%5C%22%3Eprivate%20investment%20has%20stagnated%3C%2Fa%3E%20through%20Modi%E2%80%99s%2010-year%20tenure.%20The%20finance%20minister%20herself%20has%20been%20exhorting%20domestic%20industry%20to%20start%20investing%20in%20fresh%20capacity.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%20incomes%2C%20consumption%20and%20private%20investment%20have%20broadly%20stagnated.%20There%20has%20also%20been%20a%20sharp%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Fopinion%2Fhow-serious-is-the-fall-in-household-savings%2Farticle67345771.ece%5C%22%3Efall%20in%20household%20savings%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20recent%20years%20as%20real%20incomes%20have%20declined.%20These%20facts%20cannot%20be%20controverted%20even%20by%20whatever%20limited%20data%20is%20coming%20out%20of%20the%20department%20of%20statistics.%20It%20is%20possible%20that%20in%20future%20even%20these%20data%20sets%20may%20cease%20to%20exist!%20The%20average%20GDP%20growth%20under%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20tenure%20so%20far%20is%205.8%25%20and%20many%20economists%2C%20including%20Arvind%20Subramanian%2C%20the%20Chief%20Economic%20Advisor%20in%20NDA%20I%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thehindubusinessline.com%2Feconomy%2Findias-gdp-growth-overestimated-by-25-says-former-cea-arvind-subramanian%2Farticle27788143.ece%5C%22%3Ehave%20suggested%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20number%20could%20be%20up%20to%202%20percentage%20points%20less.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20Dr%20Pronab%20Sen%2C%20chairperson%20of%20the%20Standing%20Committee%20on%20Statistics%2C%20told%20me%20that%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Feconomy-k-shaped-household-income%5C%22%3EK-shaped%20growth%20recovery%3C%2Fa%3E%20after%20COVID-19%20has%20possibly%20resulted%20in%20a%20big%20statistical%20anomaly.%20In%20normal%20times%2C%20organised%20sector%20growth%20has%20a%20positive%20correlation%20with%20the%20vast%20unorganised%2Finformal%20sector.%20Both%20grow%20together.%20But%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20COVID-19%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20has%20shown%20a%20rebound%20but%20the%20unorganised%20sector%20continued%20to%20suffer.%20The%20positive%20correlation%20broke%20down.%20This%20leads%20Sen%20to%20conclude%20that%20the%20GDP%20growth%20number%20could%20be%20overestimated%20because%20in%20the%20Indian%20system%2C%20the%20organised%20sector%20data%20available%20with%20the%20corporate%20affairs%20ministry%20is%20used%20to%20extrapolate%20for%20growth%20in%20the%20vast%20unorganised%20segment.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESo%2C%20the%20GDP%20number%20has%20also%20been%20suspect%20for%20a%20long%20time.%20Most%20budget%20numbers%20are%20predicated%20on%20the%20nominal%20GDP%20stock.%20If%20the%20GDP%20number%20is%20flawed%2C%20many%20other%20related%20figures%20and%20ratios%20will%20also%20be%20faulty.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOf%20course%2C%20all%20this%20does%20not%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20finance%20minister%20Sitharaman%20making%20hyperbolic%20claims%20of%20India%20being%20the%20biggest%20growth%20story%20in%20the%20world%20with%20rising%20incomes%2C%20consumption%2C%20investment%20and%20employment.%20The%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Feconomy%2Funpaid-labour-on-the-rise-muslims-not-looking-for-work-what-the-plfs-data-reveals%5C%22%3EPLFS%20survey%3C%2Fa%3E%20also%20shows%20a%20huge%20growth%20in%20the%20number%20of%20self-employed%20%E2%80%93%20from%2052%25%20of%20the%20total%20employed%20in%202017-18%20to%2058%25%20in%202022-23.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELabour%20economist%20Santosh%20Mehrotra%20reckons%20the%20growing%20army%20of%20self-employed%20constitutes%20very%20low%20quality%20employment%20and%20among%20them%20the%20number%20of%20unpaid%20workers%20has%20increased%20from%2040%20million%20in%202017-18%20to%2095%20million%20in%202022-23.%20Unpaid%20workers%20are%20not%20treated%20as%20formally%20employed%20by%20the%20International%20Labour%20Organisation.%20No%20wonder%20the%20finance%20minister%E2%80%99s%20speech%20hardly%20devoted%20even%20a%20paragraph%20on%20employment%20strategy.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ciframe%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fflo.uri.sh%2Fvisualisation%2F16678910%2Fembed%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Interactive%20or%20visual%20content%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fvisualisation%2F16678910%2F%3Futm_source%3Dembed%26utm_campaign%3Dvisualisation%2F16678910%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_top%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Made%20with%20Flourish%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fpublic.flourish.studio%2Fresources%2Fmade_with_flourish.svg%5C%22%3E%20%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20is%20the%20nature%20of%20the%20political%20economy%20that%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20has%20created%20before%20seeking%20his%20third%20term%20as%20a%20%E2%80%9Cdevelopment%20messiah%E2%80%9D.%20Privately%2C%20he%20probably%20recognises%20the%20distress%20among%20the%20bottom%2060%25%20of%20the%20population%20and%20has%2C%20therefore%2C%20chosen%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.narendramodi.in%2Ffree-foodgrains-for-8135-crore-beneficiaries-for-five-years-cabinet-decision-576404%5C%22%3Eprovide%3C%2Fa%3E%20free%20food%20to%20them%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Modi%20took%20power%20in%202014%2C%20his%20slogan%20was%20to%20move%20India%E2%80%99s%20poor%20from%20dole%20and%20entitlement%20to%20a%20framework%20of%20empowerment%20and%20partnership%20in%20growth.%20That%20objective%20clearly%20lies%20in%20tatters%2C%20notwithstanding%20a%20booming%20stock%20market%20in%20which%20a%20few%20hundred%20companies%E2%80%99%20shares%20are%20watched%20with%20bated%20breath%20by%20less%20than%207%25%20of%20the%20population.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706938202000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F03105830%2Fimage-1791.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fbudget-speech-incomes-consumption-private-investment-have-stagnated%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%E2%80%99s%20shortest%20budget%20speech%20was%20largely%20about%20reiterating%20the%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20achievements%20over%20the%20past%20decade.%20But%20facts%20have%20never%20come%20in%20the%20way%20of%20Modi's%20penchant%20for%20weaving%20self-congratulatory%20narratives.%C2%A0%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A12%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitical-economy%2Fbudget-speech-incomes-consumption-private-investment-have-stagnated%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22PeCee%20hops%20on%20to%20'Let's%20See%20You%20at%2021'%20trend%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706937991000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-107377969%2Cimgsize-20066.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fpriyanka-chopra-hops-on-to-the-lets-see-you-at-21-trend-pics-inside%2Farticleshow%2F107378006.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F107378006.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EJoining%20the%20Instagram%20trend%2C%20Priyanka%20Chopra%20shared%20nostalgic%20photos%20from%20her%2021-year-old%20self.%20In%20the%20first%2C%20she%20smiles%20directly%20into%20the%20camera%20with%2