0RTI%20reply%20explicitly%20mentioned%20that%20the%20chief%20minister%20flew%20to%20Majuli%20that%20day.%20Photographic%20evidence%20showed%20that%20he%20had%20flown%20to%20the%20river%20island%20for%20the%20BJP%E2%80%99s%2C%20activities%2C%20using%20a%20government-funded%20helicopter.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EParticipated%20in%20nomination%20filing%3Cbr%3E%5Cnrally%20of%20Shri%20Bhuban%20Gam%20for%20the%20upcoming%20Majuli%20LAC%20by-election.%3Cbr%3E%5CnA%20dynamic%20leader%2C%20Gam%20has%20been%20actively%20involved%20in%20Majuli%E2%80%99s%20growth%20story.%3Cbr%3E%5CnI%20am%20confident%20that%20people%20of%20Majuli%20will%20repose%20faith%20on%20him%20%26amp%3B%20elect%20him%20as%20their%20new%20representative.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2F1B7M2QzUdm%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2F1B7M2QzUdm%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%94%20Himanta%20Biswa%20Sarma%20(%40himantabiswa)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhimantabiswa%2Fstatus%2F1493852491867652096%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EFebruary%2016%2C%202022%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cb%3EOut%20of%20Assam%2C%20too%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20dates%20mentioned%20in%20the%20RTI%20replies%20reveal%20that%20Sarma%20used%20public%20money%20to%20campaign%20for%20the%20BJP%20outside%20the%20state%20too%2C%20including%20in%20the%20Delhi%20municipal%20elections.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EGlimpses%20of%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FVijaySankalpRoadShow%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23VijaySankalpRoadShow%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fhashtag%2FDelhiMCDElection2022%3Fsrc%3Dhash%26ref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3E%23DelhiMCDElection2022%3