red%2C%20I%20checked%20a%20few%20of%20Lahore%E2%80%99s%20music%20stores%20within%20my%20reach%20%E2%80%94%20which%20were%20on%20the%20verge%20of%20transitioning%20from%20cassettes%20to%20CDs%20%E2%80%94%20but%20no%20one%20had%20any%20idea%20about%20what%20I%20was%20looking%20for.%20Everything%20was%20changing%20fast.%20It%20seemed%20everyone%20wanted%20to%20speed%20up%20to%20match%20the%20pace%20of%20the%20new%20millennium.%20Like%20any%20millennial%2C%20I%20had%20witnessed%20the%20transformation%20from%20audiocassettes%20to%20CDs%20and%20MP3%20players%20to%20IPods%2C%20just%20in%20a%20few%20years.%20And%20here%20I%20was%2C%20an%20early%20teenager%2C%20trying%20to%20find%20something%20with%20ancient%20roots.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20few%20days%20later%2C%20when%20we%20went%20to%20a%20newly%20constructed%20shopping%20mall%2C%20I%20finally%20found%20a%20CD%20at%20a%20big%20music%20store%20%E2%80%93%20the%20album%20was%20titled%20%E2%80%9CPurvi%20Thaat%E2%80%9D.%20In%20the%20contents%2C%20the%20name%20of%20raga%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20was%20mentioned.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Ciframe%20allowfullscreen%3D%5C%22allowfullscreen%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fembed%2Fbo6gVgAs_P0%3Fsi%3DYg0vMq-uomCh0ppU%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22100%25%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22YouTube%20video%20player%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22504%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%20data-mce-type%3D%5C%22bookmark%5C%22%3E%EF%BB%BF%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fiframe%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20my%20first%20formal%20introduction%20to%20the%20Khayal.%20And%20this%20was%20my%20first%20meeting%20with%20the%20maestro%20Ustad%20Rashid%20Khan%20saheb.%20I%20remember%20weeping%20silently%20in%20my%20dimly%20lit%20room%20while%20listening%20to%20his%20rendition%20of%20Puriya%20Dhanashree%20that%20evening.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E***%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELahore%20feels%20colder%20than%20usual%20this%20early%20January%20evening.%20As%20I%20write%20these%20lines%2C%20the%2055-year-old%20ustad%20has%20slept%20an%20eternal%2