ue%20to%20discuss%20with%20U.S.%20Congress%20the%20potential%20sale%20consistent%20with%20standard%20processes%20and%20policies%20guiding%20such%20arm%20sales%20decisions.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EThere%20is%20normally%20a%20gap%20of%2020%20to%2040%20days%20between%20the%20tiered%20review%20process%20%E2%80%93%20an%20informal%20notification%20exercise%20for%20a%20proposed%20major%20arms%20sale%20%E2%80%93%20and%20the%20State%20Department%E2%80%99s%20formal%20notification%20to%20Congress.%20.%20In%20a%20January%202024%20report%20on%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsgp.fas.org%2Fcrs%2Fweapons%2FRL31675.pdf%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20Congressional%20review%20process%20for%20arms%20sales%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20the%20Congressional%20Research%20Serviced%20cited%20the%20State%20Department%20Insector%20General%20as%20noting%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20State%20Department%20generally%20will%20not%20formally%20notify%20an%20arms%20transfer%20if%20a%20member%20of%20Congress%20raises%20significant%20concerns%20by%20placing%20a%20hold%20during%20the%20informal%20review%20stage%E2%80%A6%20%5Bthough%5D%20the%20Department%20is%20not%20precluded%20from%20proceeding%20with%20an%20arms%20transfer%20subject%20to%20a%20congressional%20hold.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EPannun%20plot%20as%20problem%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ECongressional%20sources%20say%20the%20tiered%20review%20began%20in%20December%2C%20and%20resulted%20in%20a%20hold.%20%3C%2Fspan%3EThe%20fact%20that%20the%20State%20Department%20chose%20not%20to%20override%20the%20Congressional%20hold%20placed%20by%20Senator%20Cardin%20but%20to%20instead%20find%20ways%20to%20address%20the%20concerns%20he%20was%20raising%20suggests%20the%20Biden%20administration%20too%20was%20looking%20for%20ways%20to%20push%20the%20Modi%20government%20to%20properly%20address%20the%20Pannun%20matter.%20Conversations%20were%20taking%20place%20at%20various%20levels%20but%20the%20public%20airing%20of%20the%20linkage%20on%20January%2031%20appears%20to%20have%20raised%20the%20stakes%20and%20speeded%20the%20process.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EOn%20the%20morning%20of%20February%201%2C%20Shishir%20Gupta%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hindustantimes.com%2Findia-news%2Fus-congress-predator-drone-sale-india-101706762470138.html%5C%22%3Ereported%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%20the%C2%A0%3Ci%3EHindustan%20Times%3C%2Fi%3E%20that%20General%20Atomics%20%E2%80%93%C2%A0%20the%20California-based%20manufacturer%20of%20the%20drones%20%E2%80%93%20had%20been%20told%20by%20the%20State%20Department%20%E2%80%9Cthat%20the%20US%20Congress%20today%20has%20cleared%20the%20%E2%80%98tiered%20review%E2%80%99%C2%A0of%20the%2031%20MQ9B%20drone%20sale%20to%20India%20and%20%5Bthat%20an%5D%20official%20Congressional%20notification%20will%20be%20submitted%20within%2024%20hours.%E2%80%9D%20The%20company%20reportedly%20informed%20the%20Indian%20government%20of%20this%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%20%E2%80%9Cat%20the%20highest%20levels%E2%80%9D.%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22RTL%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22AR-SA%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3EMy%20sense%20is%20the%20GOI%20is%20embarrassed%2C%20not%20so%20much%20about%20the%20sale%20issue%20but%20the%20lack%20of%20resolution%20of%20the%20Pannun%20issue%E2%80%A6%2C%E2%80%9D%20the%20Washington-based%20source%20told%20this%20reporter%20on%20Thursday%2C%20hinting%20at%20the%20possibility%20that%20high%20level%20bilateral%20conversations%20may%20have%20been%20held%20soon%20after%20the%20story%20came%20out%20to%20ensure%20the%20drones%20and%20other%20weapons%20purchases%20do%20not%20become%20a%20casualty%20of%20Congressional%20opposition%2C%20foot-dragging%20or%20inter-agency%20disagreements%20over%20a%20murder%20plot%20that%20India%20has%20publicly%20committed%20itself%20to%20investigating.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3E%C2%A0%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP.png%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-300x150.png%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-1024x512.png%201024w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2023%2F12%2F01141008%2FPannun-FP-800x400.png%20800w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-687240%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22600%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3EGurpatwant%20Singh%20Pannun.%20Photo%3A%20X%2F%40SFJGenCounsel.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3ECardin%E2%80%99s%20own%20remarks%20about%20the%20seriousness%20of%20the%20Pannun%20issue%20%E2%80%93%20that%20the%20Biden%20administration%20%E2%80%9Chas%20demanded%20%E2%80%A6%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Cspan%20lang%3D%5C%22EN-US%5C%22%3Ethat%20there%20is%20accountability%20within%20India%20against%20these%20types%20of%20activities%E2%80%A6%20and%20that%20has%20to%20be%20demonstrated%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%93%20are%20a%20clear%20confirmation%20that%20the%20clearance%20process%20for%20the%20drone%20sale%20has%20involved%20some%20blunt%20speaking%20with%20the%20Modi%20government.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20his%20statement%20on%20Friday%2C%20Cardin%20emphasised%20the%20importance%20of%20human%20rights%3A%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20U.S.-India%20partnership%20plays%20a%20key%20role%20in%20Indo%20Pacific%20stability%2C%20including%20through%20regional%20mechanisms%20such%20as%20the%20Quad.%20I%20support%20deepening%20our%20bilateral%20relationship%20with%20India%20as%20long%20as%20that%20partnership%20is%20based%20on%20mutual%20trust%20and%20respect.%20Championing%20human%20rights%20and%20democratic%20values%20globally%20is%20one%20of%20my%20top%20priorities.%20Progress%20on%20these%20issues%20requires%20difficult%20discussions%20about%20our%20own%20democracy%2C%20as%20well%20as%20discussions%20with%20our%20closest%20allies%20and%20friends.%20I%20will%20continue%20raising%20human%20rights%20issues%20with%20the%20Administration%2C%20as%20well%20as%20our%20Indian%20counterparts%2C%20because%20I%20believe%20that%20our%20shared%20values%20are%20fundamental%20to%20the%20growth%20and%20longevity%20of%20our%20partnership.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Sea%20Guardian%2C%20built%20by%20US%20firm%20General%20Atomics%2C%20is%20the%20naval%20version%20of%20the%20storied%20Predator%20B%20armed%20drone%20(also%20termed%20the%20MQ-9%20Reaper)%2C%20with%20which%20the%20US%20has%20killed%20terrorists%20in%20Pakistan%2C%20Afghanistan%20and%20Yemen.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIndia%20had%20asked%20for%20the%20armed%20version%2C%20but%20Washington%20initially%20offered%20only%20the%20unarmed%20Sea%20Guardian%2C%20which%20performs%20maritime%20surveillance.%20However%2C%20the%20armed%20version%20now%20features%20in%20the%20notification%20issued%20to%20Congress.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20some%20confusion%20over%20the%20nomenclature%20of%20the%20drone%2C%20with%20even%20the%20US%20government%20using%20different%20names%20%E2%80%94%20MQ-9%2C%20MQ-9A%20and%20MQ-9B%20%E2%80%94%20apparently%20interchangeably.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETravelling%20at%20300%20kilometres%20per%20hour%20at%2050%2C000%20feet%2C%20the%20Sea%20Guardian%20flies%2014-hour%20missions%20to%20monitor%20waters%201%2C800%20kilometres%20from%20base.%20It%20sends%20imagery%20in%20real%20time%20to%20a%20ground%20control%20room%20on%20base%2C%20which%20flies%20the%20drone%20through%20a%20two-way%20data%20link.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20a%C2%A0%3Cspan%20dir%3D%5C%22RTL%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22AR-SA%5C%22%3E%E2%80%9C%3C%2Fspan%3ECategory%201%E2%80%9D%20system%20under%20the%20Missile%20Technology%20Control%20Regime%20(MTCR)%2C%20Sea%20Guardians%20drones%20are%20tightly%20controlled%20because%20of%20their%20presumed%20ability%20to%20deliver%20nuclear%20weapons.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22auto%5C%22%3E%3Cb%3EBiden%E2%80%99s%20tightrope%20walk%3C%2Fb%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Biden%20administration%20has%20so%20far%20walked%20a%20tightrope%20between%20the%20strategic%20imperative%20of%20getting%20the%20Indian%20military%20to%20work%20more%20closely%20with%20it%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20the%20concerns%20raised%20by%20its%20own%20officials%20about%20issues%20relating%20to%20religious%20freedom%20and%20human%20rights.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAgainst%20this%20backdrop%2C%20the%20Pannun%20murder%20plot%20has%20added%20a%20new%20complexity%20to%20the%20equation.%20Unlike%20in%20India%2C%20federal%20prosecutors%20are%20usually%20not%20known%20to%20follow%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20instructions%20on%20how%20to%20handle%20a%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20clearly%20want%20the%20issue%20to%20go%20away%20but%20it%20is%20not%20clear%20what%20assurances%2C%20if%20any%2C%20the%20Modi%20government%20has%20given%20about%20its%20promised%20investigation%20or%20what%20demands%20the%20Biden%20administration%20is%20making.%20Senator%20Cardin%2C%20who%20has%20flagged%20the%20case%20as%20crucial%2C%20will%20exit%20the%20Senate%20next%20year%2C%20having%20said%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%20noreferrer%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.politico.com%2Fnews%2F2023%2F05%2F01%2Fcardin-not-running-for-reelection-