20ran%20a%20car%20sale%20purchase%20business%2C%20which%20yielded%20good%20results%20opening%20doors%20to%20further%20opportunities.%20As%20per%20Sukh%20Gill%20Moga%2C%20a%20farmer%20leader%2C%20Satnam%20Sandhu%20also%20remained%20close%20to%20Shiromani%20Akali%20Dal%20(SAD)%20leader%20and%20ex-minister%20Jathedar%20Tota%20Singh%2C%20who%20taught%20him%20lessons%20in%20politics%20and%20public%20service.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESandhu%C2%A0launched%20the%20Chandigarh%20Group%20of%20Colleges%20at%20Landran%20village%20in%20Mohali%20district%20near%20Chandigarh%20in%202001.%20Later%20he%20formed%20Chandigarh%20University%20in%202012.%20Within%20a%20span%20of%2010%20years%2C%20Chandigarh%20University%20found%20a%20place%20in%20QS%20World%20Rankings%202023%2C%20making%20it%20first%20among%20private%20universities%20in%20Asia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20Chandigarh%20University%20hit%20the%20national%20headlines%20in%202022%2C%20when%20a%20female%20hosteller%20was%20arrested%20over%20complaints%20by%20fellow%20hostellers%20that%20she%20had%20been%20recording%20their%20videos%20in%20the%20hostel%20washrooms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EFurman%20Singh%20Sandhu%2C%20president%20of%20BKU%2C%20Punjab%20lauds%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0was%20not%20available%20for%20comments%20despite%20repeated%20attempts%20by%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20his%20brother%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0spoke%20at%20length%20about%20various%20issues.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption%5C%22%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20709px)%2085vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%20909px)%2067vw%2C%20(max-width%3A%201362px)%2062vw%2C%20840px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn.jpg%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221000%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn.jpg%201000w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn-300x176.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213141%2FGFEsqFUaUAAB3Hn-425x250.jpg%20425w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-695451%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22586%5C%22%3E%3Cp%20class%3D%5C%22wp-caption-text%5C%22%3ESatnam%20Singh%20Sandhu%20with%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi.%20Photo%20X%20(Twitter)%2F%40narendramodi.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20was%20a%20matter%20of%20pride%20that%20PM%20Modi%20sent%20his%20brother%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20who%20was%20the%20son%20of%20a%20farmer%2C%20a%20Sikh%20face%20and%20came%20from%20a%20poor%20background.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20PM%20Modi%20is%20doing%20something%20good%2C%20I%20think%2C%20we%20should%20appreciate%20him.%20He%20expressed%20his%20large%20heartedness%20and%20repealed%20the%20three%20farm%20laws.%20My%20brother%20has%20also%20written%20a%20book%20on%20PM%20Modi%E2%80%99s%20initiatives%20and%20the%20way%20he%20has%20been%20working%20for%20the%20welfare%20of%20the%20Sikhs%20in%20the%20country%2C%20it%20is%20worth%20lauding%2C%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20when%20asked%20that%20he%20was%20a%20member%20of%20SKM%20and%20the%20farmer%20leaders%20were%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20at%20Delhi%20against%20the%20Modi%20government%2C%20he%20said%2C%20%E2%80%9CWe%20will%20rethink.%20PM%20Modi%20has%20honored%20my%20brother%20and%20our%20family.%20I%20am%20with%20my%20brother.%20In%20fact%20all%20the%2032%20farmer%20union%20bodies%20have%20congratulated%20us%20on%20this%20achievement.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20is%20not%20important%20to%20hold%20protests%2C%20one%20can%20get%20their%20demands%20fulfilled%20by%20being%20in%20the%20government%20too.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFurman%20Singh%20said%20earlier%20that%20BKU%20Punjab%20president%20Bhupinder%20Singh%20Mann%20was%20also%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20He%20said%20that%20all%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20have%20different%20ideologies%20and%20they%20had%20never%20interfered%20with%20anybody%E2%80%99s%20choice%20of%20vote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CEven%20the%20India%20bloc%20has%20many%20comrades%20in%20it.%20They%20are%20political%20too.%20They%20will%20be%20going%20across%20the%20country%20to%20convey%20that%20PM%20Modi%20was%20not%20good%20for%20the%20country%2C%20then%20what%3F%20Look%20how%20Modi%20took%20difficult%20decisions%20for%20the%20betterment%20of%20the%20country%20%E2%80%93%20demonetisation%2C%20abrogation%20of%20Article%20370%20and%20the%20construction%20of%20the%20Ram%20Mandir.%20These%20are%20big%20achievements%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20listed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20a%20query%20that%20minorities%20were%20under%20attack%20and%20Sikhs%20were%20quite%20often%20branded%20as%20Khalistanis%20and%20terrorists%20by%20the%20BJP%20leaders%2C%20Furman%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0said%2C%20%E2%80%9CSuch%20small%20issues%20keep%20on%20happening.%20When%20it%20comes%20to%20law%20and%20order%2C%20one%20has%20to%20take%20strict%20decisions.%20There%20are%20many%20anti-India%20forces%2C%20which%20try%20to%20weaken%20the%20country%20and%20Modi%20has%20been%20acting%20against%20them.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EInterestingly%2C%20during%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0was%20one%20among%20those%20farmer%20union%20leaders%20who%20led%20campaigns%20across%20the%20country%20telling%20people%20to%20vote%20for%20anyone%20except%20the%20BJP.%20Furman%20had%20been%20critical%20of%20the%20BJP%20and%20its%20oppressive%20approach%20towards%20the%20farmers%20in%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESKM%20responds%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAn%20SKM%20leader%20requesting%20anonymity%20said%20Furman%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Sandhu%C2%A0led%20the%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%20at%20Delhi%20borders%20and%20he%20is%20a%20member%20of%20the%20SKM.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20this%20move%20has%20come%20at%20a%20time%20when%20farmers%20led%20by%20SKM%20(Apolitical)%20leader%20Jagjit%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Dallewal%20and%20Sarwan%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0Pandher%20from%20Kisan%20Mazdoor%20Sangharsh%20Committee%20(KMSC)%20were%20gearing%20up%20for%20the%20February%2013%20protest%20at%20Delhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20have%20been%20observing%20all%20these%20developments.%20The%20Modi%20government%20wants%20to%20create%20division%20and%20confusion%20within%20the%20SKM%20through%20this%20move.%20We%20will%20have%20to%20rethink%20this%2C%20as%20Furman%20is%20a%20member%20of%20SKM%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20SKM%20leader%20also%20shared%20that%20during%20farmers%E2%80%99%20protest%2C%20the%20agitated%20farmers%20had%20got%20a%20Modi%20government%E2%80%99s%20event%20at%20Chandigarh%20University%20cancelled%20at%20the%20last%20minute.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPolitical%20observers%20question%20nomination%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%20this%20is%20not%20the%20first%20time%20that%20the%20chancellor%20of%20a%20private%20varsity%20was%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20Earlier%20the%20Aam%20Admi%20Party%20(AAP)%20government%20in%20Punjab%20had%20nominated%20Lovely%20Professional%20University%20(LPU)%2C%20Phagwara%20founder%20chancellor%20Ashok%20Mittal%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20which%20had%20led%20to%20major%20debate%20in%20the%20public.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMany%20political%20observers%20were%20of%20the%20view%20that%20the%20rise%20of%20private%20universities%20and%20corporate%20culture%20was%20in%20sync%20with%20the%20corporate%20style%20of%20Indian%20politics%20these%20days.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETalking%20to%C2%A0%3Cem%3EThe%20Wire%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20professor%20of%20political%20science%20from%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20Professor%20Khalid%20Mohammed%20said%20that%20one%20should%20see%20the%20spirit%20of%20the%20constitution%2C%20which%20says%20that%20the%20person%20can%20be%20from%20any%20field%20but%20he%20or%20she%20should%20be%20neutral.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COver%20the%20years%2C%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20has%20become%20politically%20dead.%20It%20became%20a%20house%2C%20where%20either%20those%20who%20lost%20elections%20or%20those%20who%20aligned%20with%20the%20government%20in%20power%20were%20getting%20nominated.%20In%C2%A0Satnam%C2%A0Sandhu%E2%80%99s%20case%2C%20it%20is%20an%20example%20of%20a%20corporate%20and%20political%20lobby.%20The%20centuries%20old%20Panjab%20University%20(PU)%2C%20Chandigarh%20is%20a%20name%20to%20reckon%20with%20and%20has%20been%20performing%20far%20better%20than%20Chandigarh%20University%20but%20how%20many%20people%20from%20the%20PU%20were%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%3F%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKhalid%20said%20that%20the%20government%20could%20have%20considered%20renowned%20scientists%2C%20scholars%2C%20researchers%2C%20and%20academicians%20from%20Punjab%2C%20who%20have%20decades%20of%20excellent%20work%20to%20their%20credit%20for%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%20but%20the%20government%E2%80%99s%20idea%20is%20to%20promote%20private%20institutions.%20%E2%80%9CSatnam%20Sandhu%20made%20it%20big%20in%20life%20by%20raising%20a%20private%20university%20but%20his%20rise%20in%20this%20field%20and%20the%20support%20for%20government%20in%20power%20was%20intermixed.%20It%20definitely%20raises%20a%20question%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERenowned%20Sociologist%20from%20Panjab%20University%2C%20Chandigarh%20Professor%20Manjit%C2%A0Singh%C2%A0said%20that%20it%20is%20hardly%20a%20secret%20that%20the%20BJP%20has%20been%20desperately%20trying%20to%20rope%20in%20Sikh%20faces%20into%20its%20party%20fold%20in%20Punjab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThough%20Satnam%20Singh%20Sandhu%20has%20been%20nominated%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20he%20has%20been%20promoting%20Modi%20and%20the%20BJP%20on%20all%20his%20social%20media%20accounts.%20After%20his%20nomination%2C%20among%20those%20who%20first%20congratulated%20him%20was%20PM%20Modi.%20Let%20us%20not%20forget%20that%20whatever%20BJP%20does%2C%20it%20is%20political%20in%20every%20sense.%20Sandhu%E2%80%99s%20nomination%2C%20despite%20having%20been%20done%20by%20the%20President%20of%20India%2C%20is%20nothing%20but%20a%20political%20move%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EProfessor%20Manjit%20also%20said%20that%20there%20were%20many%20renowned%20Sikh%20figures%2C%20scientists%20and%20educationists%20from%20renowned%20universities%20of%20Punjab%2C%20who%20could%20have%20been%20nominated%20to%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%20%E2%80%9CWhen%20PM%20or%20President%20of%20India%20start%20visiting%20private%20universities%2C%20it%20gives%20legitimacy%20to%20private%20and%20corporate%20institutions.%20It%20is%20harsh%20truth%20that%20political%20parties%20need%20huge%20money%20to%20contest%20elections%20and%20supporting%20private%20ventures%20helps%20them%20in%20furthering%20their%20agendas%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706890181000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F02%2F02213534%2FEffect-96.png%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatnam-singh-sandhu-why-the-newly-nominated-rajya-sabha-mp-has-become-a-talking-point%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20Punjab%20educationist%2C%20who%20was%20recently%20nominated%20to%20Rajya%20Sabha%20by%20President%20Droupadi%20Murmu%2C%20has%20been%20point%20of%20discussion%20both%20among%20'corporate-political'%20lobby%20and%20farmers'%20unions%20too.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A5%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fsatnam-singh-sandhu-why-the-newly-nominated-rajya-sabha-mp-has-become-a-talking-point%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22BJP%20Demands%20Congress'%20Apology%20on%20MP's%20'Separate%20Country'%20Remark%20As%20Opposition%20Walks%20Out%20Over%20Jharkhand%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22161919%2F2020_9img22_Sep_2020_PTI22-09-2020_000056B.jpg%5C%22%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ENew%20Delhi%3A%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EOpposition%20members%20of%20the%20INDIA%20alliance%20staged%20a%20walkout%20in%20both%20houses%20of%20Parliament%20during%20the%20first%20half%20of%20the%20session%20on%20Friday%20(February%202)%20over%20the%20delay%20in%20government%20formation%20in%20Jharkhand%20as%20Treasury%20benches%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress%20by%20demanding%20an%20apology%20for%20its%20Lok%20Sabha%20MP%20D.K.%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20remark%20on%20a%20separate%20country%20for%20South%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha%2C%20leader%20of%20the%20house%20Piyush%20Goyal%20raised%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement%20from%20Thursday%20in%20which%20he%20critcised%20the%20Union%20government%20on%20Thursday%20and%20said%20that%20the%20people%20of%20South%20India%20might%20have%20to%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Ftax-injustice-may-compel-south-india-to-demand-a-separate-country-congress-mp-d-k-suresh%5C%22%3E%20demand%20a%20separate%20country%3C%2Fa%3E%20if%20%E2%80%9Cthe%20injustice%20of%20not%20providing%20the%20rightful%20share%20of%20taxes%20(to%20the%20southern%20states)%20continued%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CDoes%20the%20unity%20of%20the%20country%20matter%20to%20the%20Congress%3F%20Does%20it%20want%20to%20divide%20the%20country%20into%20the%20north%20and%20south%3F%20I%20demand%20an%20explanation%20from%20the%20Congress%20party.%20I%20condemn%20the%20Congress%20party%E2%80%99s%20thinking%20and%20demand%20an%20apology%20from%20the%20party%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Goyal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ELeader%20of%20opposition%20in%20the%20house%20and%20Congress%20president%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%20said%20that%20Suresh%20is%20not%20a%20member%20of%20the%20Rajya%20Sabha.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CSecond%2C%20I%20saw%20on%20television%20that%20he%20said%20that%20he%20has%20not%20made%20such%20a%20statement.%20But%20if%20he%20has%20said%20so%2C%20let%20the%20Privileges%20Committee%20investigate%20him.%20Third%2C%20if%20anyone%20talks%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%20we%20will%20never%20tolerate%20it%20whether%20they%20are%20from%20our%20party%20or%20anyone%20else%E2%80%99s.%20Whether%20anyone%20says%20or%20not%2C%20I%20am%20saying%20%E2%80%93%20I%2C%20Mallikarjun%20Kharge%2C%20from%20Kanyakumari%20to%20Kashmir%20this%20country%20is%20one.%20This%20is%20the%20reason%20Indira%20Gandhi%20gave%20her%20life%2C%20and%20so%20did%20Rajiv%20Gandhi.%20Will%20such%20a%20party%20ever%20talk%20about%20breaking%20this%20country%3F%20But%20what%20has%20not%20been%20said%20in%20this%20house%20should%20not%20be%20repeated%20here%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKharge%20then%20raised%20the%20issue%20of%20government%20formation%20in%20Jharkhand%20and%20alleged%20that%20the%20Constitution%20is%20being%20destroyed%2C%20by%20not%20allowing%20the%20new%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20Champai%20Soren%20(who%20took%20oath%20on%20Friday%20noon)%20to%20form%20the%20government%20immediately%20following%20the%20arrest%20of%20former%20chief%20minister%20Hemant%20Soren%20by%20the%20Enforcement%20Directorate%20in%20an%20alleged%20land%20scam%20case.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIn%20Jharkhand%20an%20issue%20has%20come%20up.%20The%20chief%20minister%20resigned%20and%20immediately%20named%20his%20successor%20and%20gave%20a%20list%20of%20his%20supporters%20including%20nearly%2043%20signatures%20and%20seven%20people%20were%20outside.%20He%20(governor%20CP%20Radhakrishnan)%20did%20not%20make%20any%20arrangement%20for%20that.%20We%20have%20been%20in%20politics%20and%20so%20have%20you.%20Usually%20what%20happens%20immediately%20is%20that%20until%20an%20alternate%20arrangement%20is%20made%2C%20he%20is%20continued%20and%20you%20call%20the%20leader%20and%20ask%20him%20to%20take%20on%20a%20vote%20of%20confidence.%20But%20in%20this%20case%20the%20governor%20has%20given%2010%20days%20time%20for%20the%20vote%20of%20confidence%20and%20today%20he%20will%20take%20oath%20at%2012.30pm.%20See%20how%20the%20Constitution%20is%20being%20destroyed%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPointing%20to%20Bihar%2C%20where%20chief%20minister%20Nitish%20Kumar%20on%20Sunday%20ended%20the%20alliance%20with%20RJD%20and%20formed%20the%20JDU-BJP%20government%2C%20and%20took%20oath%20as%20the%20chief%20minister%20again%20on%20the%20same%20day%2C%20Kharge%20asked%20why%20the%20government%20formation%20is%20being%20delayed%20in%20Jharkhand.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20Nitish%20Kumar%20can%20take%20oath%20in%20minutes%20in%20Bihar%20and%20he%20can%20become%20chief%20minister%20again%2C%20why%20is%20this%20happening%20in%20Jharkhand%3F%20If%20resignation%2C%20acceptance%20of%20letters%20of%20support%20and%20swearing-in%20can%20happen%20in%2012%20hours%20in%20Bihar%2C%20why%20not%20in%20Jharkhand%3F%20This%20is%20shameful.%20This%20is%20destroying%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EGoyal%20then%20said%20that%20he%20was%20surprised%20that%20the%20Congress%20was%20defending%20the%20Jharkhand%20chief%20minister%20whose%20hand%20in%20a%20scam%20has%20been%20exposed.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20way%20such%20a%20big%20corruption%20scam%20has%20been%20exposed%20in%20Jharkhand%20in%20which%20the%20chief%20minister%20has%20done%20a%20%3Cem%3Eghotala%20(%3C%2Fem%3Escam)%20in%20connection%20with%20land%2C%20I%20am%20surprised%20that%20the%20Congress%20is%20still%20defending%20him.%20The%20Congress%20is%20not%20saying%20anything%20against%20corruption%20and%20this%20shows%20that%20corruption%20is%20in%20the%20Congress%E2%80%99%20DNA.%20The%20conduct%20of%20the%20governor%20cannot%20be%20discussed%20in%20this%20house%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EINDIA%20alliance%20members%20then%20staged%20a%20walkout%20in%20protest.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBRS%20MP%20K.%20Keshava%20Rao%20then%20stood%20up%20and%20said%20that%20he%20had%20met%20Rajya%20Sabha%20chairman%20Jagdeep%20Dhankar%20on%20Friday%20morning%20prior%20to%20the%20session%20starting%20and%20enquired%20about%20the%20notification%20that%20stated%20that%20Soren%20wanted%20to%20continue%20as%20chief%20minister%20till%20an%20alternative%20arrangement%20is%20made.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20Constitution%20says%20that%20there%20has%20to%20be%20a%20government%20and%20the%20government%20has%20to%20be%20headed%20by%20a%20chief%20minister.%20Whether%20the%20chief%20minister%20is%20this%20man%20or%20that%20man%2C%20we%20are%20not%20bothered-whether%20Nitish%20goes%20in%205%20minutes%20or%20ten%20minutes.%20There%20was%20no%20need%20for%20them%20to%20walkout%20if%20you%20could%20tell%20us%20that%20there%20was%20a%20notification%2C%20there%20was%20a%20note%20that%20the%20particular%20chief%20minister%20who%20had%20resigned%20wants%20to%20continue%20till%20the%20next%20arrangement%20is%20made%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDhankar%20said%20that%20he%20did%20not%20say%20that%20he%20has%20the%20notification%20and%20only%20said%20that%20he%20will%20look%20into%20whether%20it%20was%20there.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIf%20it%20is%20not%20there%20then%20my%20point%20remains%20that%20this%20country%20has%20to%20run%20through%20a%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20Rao.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMeanwhile%20the%20Treasury%20benches%20again%20attempted%20to%20deflect%20the%20issue%20by%20bringing%20up%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWhen%20there%20is%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20member%20of%20the%20other%20house%20talking%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%2C%20we%20are%20being%20told%20that%20you%20cannot%20take%20it%20up%20on%20technical%20grounds.%20But%20we%20are%20happily%20discussing%20the%20conduct%20of%20a%20governor%20who%20knows%20his%20position.%20And%20the%20walkout%20is%20in%20favour%20of%20corruption%2C%E2%80%9D%20said%20finance%20minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CThe%20entire%20opposition%20has%20walked%20out%20in%20favour%20of%20corruption%20rather%20than%20saying%20why%20they%20want%20to%20walkout.%20We%20cannot%20speak%20about%20the%20member%20of%20the%20other%20house%20talking%20about%20breaking%20the%20country%2C%20but%20here%20they%20are%20questioning%20the%20functioning%20of%20the%20governor.%20This%20kind%20of%20conduct%20against%20a%20constitutional%20authority%20by%20a%20party%20who%20has%20been%20in%20power%20for%2045-50%20years%20is%20despicable.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20questioning%20of%20the%20governor%E2%80%99s%20conduct%20particularly%20when%20it%20is%20on%20the%20issue%20of%20corruption%20by%20the%20Congress%20is%20astonishing%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20opposition%20MPs%20also%20staged%20a%20brief%20walkout%20over%20the%20Jharkhand%20issue%2C%20with%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20led%20the%20charge%20against%20the%20Congress%20over%20Suresh%E2%80%99s%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20the%20charge%20was%20led%20by%20Union%20Parliamentary%20Affairs%20minister%20Pralhad%20Joshi%2C%20who%20said%20that%20Suresh%20had%20made%20the%20excuse%20of%20taxation%20and%20spoke%20about%20dividing%20the%20country.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20condemn%20his%20statement.%20Demanding%20the%20division%20of%20the%20Congress%20has%20been%20the%20tradition%20of%20the%20Congress.%20The%20party%20should%20explain%20its%20stand%20and%20aplogise%20to%20the%20nation%20for%20insulting%20the%20Constitution%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20also%20asked%20for%20the%20matter%20to%20be%20sent%20to%20the%20Ethics%20Committee%20and%20demanded%20the%20Congress%20to%20act%20on%20Suresh%20and%20demanded%20an%20apology%20from%20Sonia%20Gandhi.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20opposition%20then%20staged%20a%20brief%20walkout%20ahead%20of%20the%20discussion%20on%20the%20motion%20of%20thanks%20on%20the%20President%E2%80%99s%20speech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20tweet%20on%20X%20(formerly%20Twitter)%20TMC%20MP%20Derek%20O%E2%80%99Brien%20stated%20that%20the%20TMC%20had%20walked%20out%20of%20both%20houses%20over%20the%20%E2%80%9Cbrazen%20misuse%20of%20agencies%20to%20undermine%20elected%20representatives.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706887611000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thewire.in%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2020%2F09%2F22161919%2F2020_9img22_Sep_2020_PTI22-09-2020_000056B.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-demands-congress-apology-on-mps-separate-country-remark-as-opposition-walks-out-over-jharkhand%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20houses%20of%20parliament%20saw%20the%20opposition%20and%20the%20Treasury%20Benches%20cross%20swords%20over%20D.K.%20Suresh%20and%20delay%20in%20government%20formation%20in%20Jharkhand.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A7%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fthewire.in%2Fpolitics%2Fbjp-demands-congress-apology-on-mps-separate-country-remark-as-opposition-walks-out-over-jharkhand%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Floating%20sauna%20guests%20wearing%20only%20towels%20rescue%20duo%20after%20car%20plunges%20into%20fjord%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706884980000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fe3.365dm.com%2F24%2F02%2F768x432%2Fskynews-oslo-norway-car-rescue_6442178.jpg%3F20240202174650%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky.com%2Fstory%2Ffloating-sauna-guests-wearing-only-towels-rescue-duo-after-car-plunges-into-oslo-fjord-13062233%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Guests%20on%20board%20a%20floating%20sauna%20helped%20rescue%20two%20people%20after%20their%20car%20plunged%20off%20a%20quay%20into%20a%20fjord%20in%20Oslo.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A67%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fnews.sky