d%20water%20over%20the%20expectations%20of%20the%20people%20of%20this%20country%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Priyanka%20Chaturvedi%2C%20leader%20Shiv%20Sena%20(UBT).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%2C%20in%20a%20televised%20address%20following%20the%20budget%2C%20said%20it%20will%20empower%20the%20four%20pillars%20of%20developed%20India%2C%20namely%20the%20young%2C%20poor%2C%20women%20and%20farmers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20is%20a%20budget%20of%20creating%20India's%20future%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20it%20is%20a%20reflection%20of%20the%20young%20aspirations%20of%20a%20young%20India.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%2C%20Congress'%20leader%20in%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%2C%20said%20the%20budget%20only%20aims%20to%20woo%20people%20ahead%20of%20polls.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIs%20this%20a%20budget%20to%20provide%20employment%20to%20the%20unemployed...%20This%20budget%20is%20nothing%20but%20to%20woo%20people%20in%20this%20year's%20Lok%20Sabha%20elections%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Mr%20Chowdhury.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Finance%20Minister%20took%20a%20long%20time%20to%20hail%20praises%20but%20delivery%20was%20zero.%20They%20are%20going%20to%20present%20a%20white%20paper%20on%20the%20previous%20government...%20Nothing%20much%20has%20happened%20in%20the%20last%2010%20years.%20The%20people%20of%20the%20country%20are%20already%20disappointed.%20Moreover%2C%20you%20realise%20that%20performance%20incentives%20are%20given%20to%20the%20bridge%20companies%2C%20and%20not%20going%20to%20the%20deserving%20ones.%20People%20are%20rejected%20with%20this%20budget%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20DMK%20MP%20Dayanidhi%20Maran.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BMere%20administrative%20exercise%20to%20ensure%20that%20the%20government%20of%20India%20has%20the%20requisite%20funds%20to%20carry%20on%20its%20normal%20business%20until%20the%20new%20parliament%20is%20constituted%20and%20a%20new%20government%20is%20formed.%20And%20that's%20what%20they%20have%20done%2C%20except%20for%20making%20their%20obligatory%20self-congratulatory%2C%20self-praise%20phrases%2C%20nothing%20else%20is%20there%20and%20nothing%20should%20have%20been%20there%2C%20and%20rightly%20so.%20Nothing%20is%20there%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Congress%20MP%20Karti%20Chidambaram.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1706776140000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-02%2Fu1706ego_nirmala-_625x300_01_February_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Ffarewell-budget-opposition-reacts-to-nirmala-sitharamans-interim-budget-4972834%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20promised%20economic%20reforms%20to%20drive%20growth%20in%20a%20speech%20on%20the%20government's%20budget%20on%20Thursday%2C%20the%20last%20before%20a%20national%20election%20due%20by%20May.%20The%20Opposition%2C%20however%2C%20has%20termed%20it%20the%20%26quot%3Bvidai%20(farewell)%20budget%26quot%3B.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Ffarewell-budget-opposition-reacts-to-nirmala-sitharamans-interim-budget-4972834%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Ffarewell-budget-opposition-reacts-to-nirmala-sitharamans-interim-budget-4972834%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbusiness-news%2Ffarewell-budget-opposition-reacts-to-nirmala-sitharamans-interim-budget-4972834%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Tax%20Slab%20Trends%20In%20Interim%20Budgets%3A%20Why%20They%20Don't%20Change%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20interim%20Budget%20this%20Lok%20Sabha%20election%20year%20did%20not%20make%20any%20changes%20in%20tax%20slabs%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20only%20announced%20relief%20for%20old%20and%20disputed%20tax%20demands%2