0anyone%20until%20it%20was%20known%20that%20the%20team%20of%20four%20was%20using%20the%20property%20to%20produce%20%26quot%3Bfine-quality%26quot%3B%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drugs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20lab%20at%20the%20%26quot%3Bluxurious%20and%20lonely%20private%20place%26quot%3B%20at%20Alestonia%20Estate%20in%20Uttar%20Pradesh's%20Greater%20Noida%20was%20busted%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20on%20Tuesday.%20The%20police%20recovered%20445%20grams%20of%20fine-quality%20banned%20methamphetamine%20drug%20and%2020.5%20kg%20of%20raw%20materials%20that%20included%20one%20kg%20of%20pseudoephedrine%20-%20an%20ingredient%20for%20the%20illicit%20manufacture%20of%20methamphetamines.%20Sophisticated%20equipment%2C%20including%20a%20heating%20mantle%20machine%20and%20high-quality%20face%20masks%2C%20were%20also%20recovered%20from%20the%20lab.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENigerian%20national%20Eze%20Uchenna%20James%20(49)%2C%20Alitumo%20Ifedi%20Shedrack%20(28)%2C%20Eze%20Ibe%20Emeka%20Chibuzo%20alias%20Iko%20(56)%20and%20Kenyan%20national%20Ivo%20Osita%20alias%20Usta%20alias%20Osey%20(44)%20have%20been%20arrested%2C%20police%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20the%20accused%2C%20Eze%2C%20Alitumo%20and%20Ivo%20were%20previously%20arrested%20and%20convicted%20in%20drug%20trafficking%20cases%20and%20were%20out%20on%20conditional%20bail%2C%20according%20to%20Deputy%20Commissioner%20of%20Police%20(Dwarka)%20Ankit%20Singh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20drug%20bust%20was%20part%20of%20an%20ongoing%20operation%20by%20the%20Delhi%20Police%20against%20the%20suppliers%20of%20narcotics%20substances.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOn%20November%2027%2C%202023%2C%20a%20team%20of%20the%20Anti-Narcotics%20Cell%20of%20Dwarka%20district%20got%20a%20secret%20tip-off%20about%20a%20Nigerian%20national%20being%20involved%20in%20a%20drug%20syndicate.%20The%20team%20conducted%20a%20raid%20and%20caught%20Eze%20from%20Uttam%20Nagar.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESoon%20after%20Eze's%20arrest%2C%20his%20associate%20Alitumo%20was