ot%20pursue%20taxpayers%20to%20recover%20old%20and%20disputed%20direct%20taxes%20up%20to%20Rs%2025%2C000%20till%20the%20financial%20year%202009-10%2C%20Finance%20Minister%20Nirmala%20Sitharaman%20said%20in%20her%20interim%20Budget%202024%20speech%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDirect%20taxes%20demand%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20from%20the%20financial%20years%202010-11%20to%202014-15%20will%20also%20be%20withdrawn%2C%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThis%20will%20benefit%20about%20one%20crore%20taxpayers%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3B...%20There%20are%20a%20large%20number%20of%20petty%2C%20non-verified%2C%20non-reconciled%20or%20disputed%20direct%20tax%20demands%2C%20many%20of%20them%20dating%20as%20far%20back%20as%201962%2C%20which%20continue%20to%20remain%20on%20the%20books%2C%20causing%20anxiety%20to%20honest%20taxpayers%20and%20hindering%20refunds%20of%20subsequent%20years.%20I%20propose%20to%20withdraw%20such%20outstanding%20direct%20tax%20demands%20up%20Rs%2025%2C000%20pertaining%20to%20the%20period%20up%20to%20financial%20year%202009-10%2C%20and%20up%20to%20Rs%2010%2C000%20for%20financial%20years%202010-11%20to%202014-15.%20This%20is%20expected%20to%20benefit%20about%20a%20crore%20taxpayers%2C%26quot%3B%20Ms%20Sitharaman%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20did%20not%20make%20changes%20to%20tax%20slabs%20in%20the%20interim%20Budget%20in%20keeping%20with%20convention.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20for%20tax%20proposals%2C%20in%20keeping%20with%20the%20convention%2C%20I%20do%20not%20propose%20to%20make%20any%20changes%20relating%20to%20taxation%20and%20propose%20to%20retain%20the%20same%20tax%20rates%20for%20direct%20taxes%20and%20indirect%20taxes%20including%20import%20duties%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHowever%2C%20certain%20tax%20benefits%20to%20start-ups%20and%20investments%20made%20by%20sovereign%20wealth%20or%20pension%20funds%20as%20also%20tax%20exemption%20on%20certain%20incom