ou-cant-use-paytm-wallet-transfers-after-feb-29-see-affected-features-4967286%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20which%20is%20part%20of%20one%20of%20India's%20largest%20payment%20firms%20Paytm%2C%20was%20told%20by%20the%20regulator%20that%20it%20will%20not%20be%20able%20to%20take%20fresh%20deposits%2C%20facilitate%20credit%20transactions%2C%20or%20offer%20fund%20transfers%2C%20including%20Unified%20Payments%20Interface%20(UPI)%20facility%20after%20February%2029.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNo%20further%20deposits%20or%20credit%20transactions%20or%20top%20ups%20shall%20be%20allowed%20in%20any%20customer%20accounts%2C%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20wallets%2C%20FASTags%2C%20NCMC%20cards%2C%20etc.%20after%20February%2029%2C%202024%2C%20other%20than%20any%20interest%2C%20cashbacks%2C%20or%20refunds%20which%20may%20be%20credited%20anytime%2C%26quot%3B%20Yogesh%20Dayal%2C%20a%20chief%20general%20manager%20with%20the%20central%20bank%2C%20said%20in%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Frbidocs.rbi.org.in%2Frdocs%2FPressRelease%2FPDFs%2FPR1774PPBLBEDADC47266E41F7A65307C63180E2B1.PDF%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Epress%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWithdrawal%20or%20utilisation%20of%20balances%20by%20its%20customers%20from%20their%20accounts%20including%20savings%20bank%20accounts%2C%20current%20accounts%2C%20prepaid%20instruments%2C%20FASTags%2C%20National%20Common%20Mobility%20Cards%2C%20etc.%20are%20to%20be%20permitted%20without%20any%20restrictions%2C%20up%20to%20their%20available%20balance%2C%20the%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20RBI%20Has%20Put%20Restrictions%20On%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%3F%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20RBI%20said%20it%20had%20in%20March%202022%20asked%20the%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20to%20stop%20adding%20new%20customers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20a%20Comprehensive%20System%20Audit%20report%20and%20subsequent%20compliance%20validation%20report%20of%20the%20external%20auditors%20revealed%20persistent%20non-compliances%20and%20continued%20material%20supervisory%20concerns%20in%20the%20bank%2C%20warranting%20further%20supervisory%20action%2C%20the%20RBI%20said%2C%20without%20disclosing%20details.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20action%20against%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Frbi-action-paytm-payments-bank-the-only-services-allowed-are-4967226%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%3C%2Fa%3E%20was%20taken%20under%20Section%2035A%20of%20the%20Banking%20Regulation%20Act%2C%201949%2C%20the%20central%20bank%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhat%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Said%20On%20RBI%20Restrictions%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh3%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPaytm%20Payments%20Bank%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20One%2097%20Communications%20Limited%20(OCL)%2C%20said%20it%20is%20taking%20%26quot%3Bimmediate%20steps%26quot%3B%20to%20comply%20with%20the%20RBI's%20directions.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOCL%2C%20as%20a%20payments%20company%2C%20works%20with%20various%20banks%20(not%20just%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank)%2C%20on%20various%20payments%20products%2C%20the%20fintech%20company%20said%20in%20a%20statement%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EUpdate%3A%20Paytm%20Payments%20Bank%20Limited%2C%20an%20associate%20of%20Paytm%20receives%20RBI%20directions.%20Paytm%20to%20expand%20its%20existing%20relationships%20with%20leading%20third-party%20banks%20to%20distribute%20payments%20and%20financial%20services%20products.%3Cbr%3E%5CnRead%20more%20here%3A%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%5C%22%3Ehttps%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FNsPCOxp6VJ%3C%2Fa%3E%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FfQjozyR11m%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FfQjozyR11m%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Paytm%20(%40Paytm)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FPaytm%2Fstatus%2F1752783857697665354%3Fref_sr