%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithais%20%3C%2Fem%3Eand%20milk%20products%2C%20Picture%20source%3A%20Harshit%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-heading%5C%22%3ETaking%20the%20legacy%20forward%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhile%20designing%20the%20brand%20identity%2C%20Harshit%20was%20clear%20that%20quality%20needed%20to%20be%20premium%2C%20which%20is%20also%20why%20Pistabarfi%20products%20retail%20at%20a%20higher%20rate%20than%20most%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20brand%20retails%20three%20products%20%E2%80%94%20%3Cem%3Epistabarfi%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20from%20crushed%20Peshawari%20pistachios%2C%20%3Cem%3Ekaju%20katli%3C%2Fem%3E%20(made%20with%20premium%20cashew%20nuts%20and%20400%20g%20of%20sugar%20in%20contrast%20to%20the%20600%20g%20variants%20in%20the%20market)%20and%20%3Cem%3Egur%20laddoo%3C%2Fem%3E%20made%20with%20%3Cem%3Ejowar%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Ebajra%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20%3Cem%3Enachni%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%20wheat%2C%20rice%2C%20jaggery%20and%20ghee.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20reason%20behind%20this%20limited%20selection%2C%20says%20Tanay%2C%20is%20quality.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20are%20very%20sure%20of%20the%20three%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%20we%20have.%20It%20takes%20a%20lot%20of%20time%20to%20do%20R%26amp%3BD%20and%20to%20crack%20the%20correct%20taste.%20Also%2C%20some%20of%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F251389%2Fholi-gujiya-thanjavur-iconic-eatery-bombay-sweets-guru-dayal-sharma-bg-subramani-sharma-sweet-maker-india-gop94%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethese%20recipes%3C%2Fa%3E%20have%20been%20carried%20down%20from%20generation%20to%20generation%20and%20that%20makes%20it%20special.%20We%20are%20looking%20to%20include%20%3Cem%3EMysore%20pak%3C%2Fem%3E%20next%2C%20trials%20for%20which%20have%20been%20underway%20for%20quite%20some%20time%20now.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnd%20their%20packaging%20parallels%20the%20%3Cem%3Emithais%3C%2Fem%3E%2