-plastic-into-sunglasses%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Ethe%20environment%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20the%20biggest%20problem%20I%20came%20across%20was%20waste.%20I%20narrowed%20it%20down%20to%20the%20micro%20level%20and%20found%20out%20that%20most%20households%20were%20either%20not%20aware%20of%20proper%20waste%20segregation%20or%20were%20too%20busy%20to%20do%20it%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20explains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20solve%20the%20problem%20of%20landfills%20and%20waste%20remaining%20unrecycled%2C%20Abhishek%20opines%20that%20there%20was%20a%20need%20to%20find%20the%20core%20issue.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9COnce%20I%20had%20recognised%20the%20issue%2C%20a%20small%20idea%20sprung%20into%20my%20head.%20I%20started%20a%20WhatsApp%20group%20where%20I%20invited%20people%20to%20segregate%20their%20waste%20and%20hand%20it%20over%20to%20me%20in%20exchange%20for%20a%20goody%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CAnd%20it%20worked!%20A%20lot%20of%20people%20showed%20so%20much%20interest%20and%20were%20willing%20to%20do%20it%20for%20a%20reward.%20It%20was%20a%20new%20and%20interesting%20concept%20for%20them%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20adds.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20was%20a%20sign%20enough%20and%20Abhishek%20decided%20to%20expand%20on%20this%20idea.%20%E2%80%9CA%20small%20family%20of%20people%2C%20everyday%20400%20to%20500%20gm%20of%20plastic%20is%20generated%20at%20home.%20There%20are%20no%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F310812%2Fmukul-chhabra-scrapuncle-delhi-startup-collects-recycles-scrap-wins-lakhs-shark-tank%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20scrap%20dealers%3C%2Fa%3E%20who%20will%20take%20that%20amount%20of%20plastic.%20I%20realised%20that%20this%20was%20a%20problem%20with%20many%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20push%20people%20to%20make%20segregating%20waste%20a%20habit%20and%20part%20of%20their%20daily%20routine%2C%20Abhishek%20decided%20t